Id`、`action`、`result`、`errorCode`、`requestId`、发生时间 | 审计日志最小字段 |\n| FR-012 | `attemptNo` 或等价执行尝试序号、内部取消标记、最终状态 | 用于证明重试不丢审计链路、取消不暴露内部状态 |\n| FR-013 | `clientRequestId`、`idempotencyScope`、`requestDigest`、`configSnapshotDigest`、`attemptNo`、`lockOwner`、`lockExpireAt`、`leaseRenewedAt` | 用于证明幂等、防重复执行、配置快照和锁租约行为 |\n| FR-006/FR-013 | `cursorField`、`lastCursor`、`processedCount`、`filePartNo`、`batchSize`、`batchRowCount`、`retryCount`、`backoffMs` | 用于证明游标分页、锁接管、批次执行和查询重试证据 |\n| FR-014 | `taskCode=purchase-order-export`、`subsystemCode=purchase`、`datasourceCode`、`queryTemplateVersion`、`createdAtRange`、`orderStatus`、`supplierId`、`purchaseOrgId`、`keyword`、字段定义、敏感字段脱敏策略、`cursorField=orderId` | 用于证明采购订单样板集中查询合同可执行 |\n| FR-008/FR-010/FR-013 | `taskId`、`attemptNo`、`requestId`、`queryTemplateVersion`、`datasourceCode`、`batchCheckpoint` | 用于证明查询执行上下文和审计串联 |\n| FR-003/FR-011 | `tempStorageKey`、`publishedStorageKey`、`checksum`、`checksumVerifiedAt`、`publishedAt`、`deliveryReadyAt` | 用于证明临时对象、发布对象、校验和下载准备状态可追踪 |\n\n## 4. 错误映射\n\n| 场景 | 对外状态 | 错误码 | 验收入口 |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| 查询模板不存在或不合法 | `FAILED` | `QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID` | AC-E011 |\n| 数据源不可用或凭证不可用 | `FAILED` | `DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE` | AC-E012 |\n| 查询执行失败 | `FAILED` | `QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR` | AC-E013 |\n| 查询批次重试耗尽 | `FAILED` | `QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR` | AC-E020 |\n| 查询模板或字段映射与任务快照冲突 | `FAILED` | `QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID` 或 `FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID` | AC-E024 |\n| 字段映射不合法 | `FAILED` | `FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID` | AC-E014 |\n| 批次字段、顺序或脱敏结果不合法 | `FAILED` | `FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID` 或 `MASKING_RULE_ERROR` | AC-E025 |\n| 脱敏规则配置或执行失败 | `FAILED` | `MASKING_RULE_ERROR` | AC-E022 |\n| 文件渲染失败 | `FAILED` | `EXPORT_RENDER_ERROR` | AC-E027 |\n| OSS 上传失败 | `FAILED` | `FILE_VERIFY_ERROR` | AC-E005 |\n| 文件发布前校验失败 | `FAILED` | `FILE_VERIFY_ERROR` | AC-E026 |\n| 采购订单游标缺失、重复或非递增 | `FAILED` | `QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR` | AC-E023 |\n\n## 5. 缺口\n\n| Gap ID | 缺口 | 处理方式 |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| GAP-001 | 样板模块字段与表头 | 采购订单导出样板覆盖订单号、订单状态、供应商、采购组织、采购员、创建时间、总金额、币种和脱敏后的联系人信息 |\n| GAP-002 | 统一认证上下文字段 | 最小字段锁定为 `operatorId`、`tenantId`、`roleCodes`、`orgScope`、`requestId`；联调只确认字段来源和透传方式 |\n| GAP-003 | 查询性能基线 | 采购订单样板以 10 万行导出作为基线证据，记录总耗时、批大小、分片数和查询重试情况 |\n| GAP-004 | OSS bucket/path、签名有效期和文件校验值生成方式 | bucket 由环境配置；path 默认 `exports/{subsystemCode}/{taskCode}/{yyyyMMdd}/{taskId}/{attemptNo}/{fileName}`；签名 URL 默认 10 分钟；校验默认 `SHA-256` |\n| GAP-005 | 采购订单样板合同是否足够驱动实现和测试 | 已锁定 taskCode、subsystemCode、查询条件、字段顺序、敏感字段、游标字段、边界数据和压测证据 |\n\r\n\n succeeded in 769ms:\nopenapi: 3.0.3\ninfo:\n  title: Export Platform API Contract\n  version: 1.0.0\n  license:\n    name: Internal\n    url: https://example.invalid/internal-license\n  description: |\n    CONTRACT-001 defines the public API contract for FEAT-EXPORT-PLATFORM-001.\n    The API consumes authentication context from upstream services and exposes\n    only official task statuses: PENDING, EXECUTING, COMPLETED, FAILED,\n    CANCELED, EXPIRED.\nservers:\n  - url: /api\n    description: Relative platform API base path\ntags:\n  - name: ExportTasks\n    description: Task creation, detail, history, download, cancel and retry APIs.\n  - name: ExportRegistries\n    description: Export task registry, enable/disable and configuration APIs.\nsecurity:\n  - OperatorId: []\n    TenantId: []\n    RoleCodes: []\n    OrgScope: []\n    RequestId: []\nx-contract-implementation-trace:\n  description: |\n    CONTRACT-REVIEW-001 requires every public operation to stay traceable to\n    later HTTP handler, persistence, worker, audit, file and test obligations.\n    Paths below are planned implementation targets, not current implementation evidence.\n  operations:\n    createExportTask:\n      http: POST /api/export/tasks\n      requirements: [FR-001, FR-009, FR-013]\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-001, AE-009, AE-014]\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/create-export-task.handler.ts\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_idempotency, export_registries, export_audit_logs]\n      worker: [scheduler must consume committed PENDING task]\n      audit: [CREATE]\n      file: []\n      tests:\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.create.contract.test.ts\n        - tests/api/export-tasks.create.api.test.ts\n        - tests/db/export-task-idempotency.repository.test.ts\n    listExportTasks:\n      http: GET /api/export/tasks\n      requirements: [FR-004, FR-009, FR-010]\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-004, AE-009, AE-010]\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/list-export-tasks.handler.ts\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_files, export_audit_logs]\n      worker: []\n      audit: [QUERY_HISTORY]\n      file: []\n      tests:\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.list.contract.test.ts\n        - tests/api/export-tasks.visibility.api.test.ts\n    getExportTask:\n      http: GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}\n      requirements: [FR-002, FR-010, FR-013]\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-002, AE-010, AE-013]\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/get-export-task.handler.ts\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_events, export_task_attempts, export_task_files]\n      worker: [batch checkpoint and lease fields are worker-produced evidence]\n      audit: [DETAIL_VIEW]\n      file: [file metadata must exclude unpublished objects]\n      tests:\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.detail.contract.test.ts\n        - tests/api/export-tasks.detail.api.test.ts\n    downloadExportTask:\n      http: GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/download\n      requirements: [FR-003, FR-009, FR-010]\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-003, AE-009, AE-021]\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/download-export-task.handler.ts\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_files, export_audit_logs]\n      worker: []\n      audit: [DOWNLOAD]\n      file: [file service must validate published object, checksum, expiry and delivery mode]\n      tests:\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.download.contract.test.ts\n        - tests/file/export-file-download.guard.test.ts\n    cancelExportTask:\n      http: POST /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/cancel\n      requirements: [FR-012, FR-010]\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-012]\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/cancel-export-task.handler.ts\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_events, export_audit_logs]\n      worker: [EXECUTING cancel closes at a persisted batch boundary]\n      audit: [CANCEL_REQUEST, CANCEL_DONE]\n      file: []\n      tests:\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.cancel.contract.test.ts\n        - tests/worker/export-task-cancel-boundary.test.ts\n    retryExportTask:\n      http: POST /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/retry\n      requirements: [FR-012, FR-013, FR-010]\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-012, AE-013]\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/retry-export-task.handler.ts\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_attempts, export_task_events, export_audit_logs]\n      worker: [retry enqueues a new attempt only for FAILED tasks]\n      audit: [RETRY_REQUEST]\n      file: []\n      tests:\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.retry.contract.test.ts\n        - tests/db/export-task-attempt.repository.test.ts\n    createExportRegistry:\n      http: POST /api/export/registries\n      requirements: [FR-007, FR-008, FR-009]\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007, AE-008, AE-016]\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/create-export-registry.handler.ts\n      db: [export_registries, export_registry_versions, export_audit_logs]\n      worker: []\n      audit: [REGISTRY_CREATE]\n      file: []\n      tests:\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.create.contract.test.ts\n        - tests/api/export-registries.create.api.test.ts\n    listExportRegistries:\n      http: GET /api/export/registries\n      requirements: [FR-007, FR-008, FR-009]\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007, AE-008]\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/list-export-registries.handler.ts\n      db: [export_registries, export_registry_versions]\n      worker: []\n      audit: [REGISTRY_QUERY]\n      file: []\n      tests:\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.list.contract.test.ts\n    getExportRegistry:\n      http: GET /api/export/registries/{taskCode}\n      requirements: [FR-007, FR-008, FR-013]\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007, AE-008, AE-016]\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/get-export-registry.handler.ts\n      db: [export_registries, export_registry_versions]\n      worker: []\n      audit: [REGISTRY_DETAIL]\n      file: []\n      tests:\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.detail.contract.test.ts\n    updateExportRegistry:\n      http: PUT /api/export/registries/{taskCode}\n      requirements: [FR-007, FR-008, FR-013]\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007, AE-008, AE-016]\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/update-export-registry.handler.ts\n      db: [export_registries, export_registry_versions, export_audit_logs]\n      worker: [updated config applies only to newly created tasks]\n      audit: [REGISTRY_UPDATE]\n      file: []\n      tests:\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.update.contract.test.ts\n        - tests/db/export-registry-snapshot.repository.test.ts\n    enableExportRegistry:\n      http: POST /api/export/registries/{taskCode}/enable\n      requirements: [FR-007]\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007]\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/enable-export-registry.handler.ts\n      db: [export_registries, export_audit_logs]\n      worker: []\n      audit: [REGISTRY_ENABLE]\n      file: []\n      tests:\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.enable.contract.test.ts\n    disableExportRegistry:\n      http: POST /api/export/registries/{taskCode}/disable\n      requirements: [FR-007]\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007]\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/disable-export-registry.handler.ts\n      db: [export_registries, export_audit_logs]\n      worker: [future create requests must fail with TASK_DISABLED]\n      audit: [REGISTRY_DISABLE]\n      file: []\n      tests:\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.disable.contract.test.ts\npaths:\n  /export/tasks:\n    post:\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\n      summary: Create export task\n      description: |\n        Creates a PENDING export task when taskCode is registered and enabled.\n        clientRequestId is idempotent in scope tenantId + operatorId + taskCode + clientRequestId.\n      operationId: createExportTask\n      parameters:\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\n      requestBody:\n        required: true\n        content:\n          application/json:\n            schema:\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/CreateExportTaskRequest\"\n            examples:\n              purchaseOrder:\n                summary: Purchase order export task\n                value:\n                  taskCode: purchase-order-export\n                  subsystemCode: purchase\n                  fileFormat: XLSX\n                  clientRequestId: req-20260513-0001\n                  queryParams:\n                    createdAtFrom: \"2026-05-01T00:00:00+08:00\"\n                    createdAtTo: \"2026-05-13T23:59:59+08:00\"\n                    orderStatus: APPROVED\n                    supplierId: SUP-001\n                    purchaseOrgId: ORG-001\n                    keyword: PO-2026\n      x-contract-errorResponses:\n        - TASK_DISABLED\n        - EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED\n        - QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID\n        - DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE\n        - FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\n        - MASKING_RULE_ERROR\n        - INTERNAL_ERROR\n      responses:\n        \"201\":\n          description: Task created.\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/CreateExportTaskResponseEnvelope\"\n              examples:\n                created:\n                  value:\n                    code: SUCCESS\n                    message: success\n                    data:\n                      taskId: exp_20260513_000001\n                      taskCode: purchase-order-export\n                      subsystemCode: purchase\n                      status: PENDING\n                      clientRequestId: req-20260513-0001\n                      idempotencyHit: false\n                      idempotencyScope: tenant-001:u001:purchase-order-export:req-20260513-0001\n                      requestDigest: sha256:request-digest\n                      configSnapshotDigest: sha256:config-digest\n                      attemptNo: 0\n                      createdAt: \"2026-05-13T10:00:00+08:00\"\n        \"200\":\n          description: Existing task returned for idempotent replay with identical request digest.\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/CreateExportTaskResponseEnvelope\"\n        \"400\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/CreateTaskBadRequest\"\n        \"401\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\n        \"403\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\n        \"404\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotRegistered\"\n        \"409\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/IdempotencyConflict\"\n        \"500\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/DatasourceUnavailable\"\n      x-contract-errorResponseStatus:\n        TASK_DISABLED: 400\n        QUERY_PARAMS_TOO_LARGE: 400\n        EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED: 400\n        DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE: 500\n        INTERNAL_ERROR: 500\n    get:\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\n      summary: Search task history\n      description: |\n        Returns paged task history. Normal users can only see their own tasks;\n        administrators can see global tasks according to roleCodes and orgScope.\n      operationId: listExportTasks\n      parameters:\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\n        - name: taskCode\n          in: query\n          schema:\n            type: string\n        - name: status\n          in: query\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/TaskStatus\"\n        - name: createdBy\n          in: query\n          schema:\n            type: string\n        - name: createdAtFrom\n          in: query\n          schema:\n            type: string\n            format: date-time\n        - name: createdAtTo\n          in: query\n          schema:\n            type: string\n            format: date-time\n        - name: fileFormat\n          in: query\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/FileFormat\"\n        - name: subsystemCode\n          in: query\n          schema:\n            type: string\n        - name: page\n          in: query\n          schema:\n            type: integer\n            minimum: 1\n            default: 1\n        - name: pageSize\n          in: query\n          schema:\n            type: integer\n            minimum: 1\n            maximum: 100\n            default: 20\n      responses:\n        \"200\":\n          description: Paged task history.\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportTaskPageEnvelope\"\n        \"401\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\n        \"403\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\n        \"500\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/QueryExecutionError\"\n  /export/tasks/{taskId}:\n    get:\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\n      summary: Get task detail and progress\n      operationId: getExportTask\n      parameters:\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskId\"\n      responses:\n        \"200\":\n          description: Task detail.\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportTaskDetailEnvelope\"\n              examples:\n                executing:\n                  value:\n                    code: SUCCESS\n                    message: success\n                    data:\n                      taskId: exp_20260513_000001\n                      taskCode: purchase-order-export\n                      subsystemCode: purchase\n                      status: EXECUTING\n                      totalCount: 100000\n                      processedCount: 20000\n                      progressPercent: 20.0\n                      fileFormat: ZIP\n                      attemptNo: 1\n                      requestId: req-20260513-0001\n                      requestDigest: sha256:request-digest\n                      configSnapshotDigest: sha256:config-digest\n                      createdBy: u001\n                      createdAt: \"2026-05-13T10:00:00+08:00\"\n                      updatedAt: \"2026-05-13T10:05:00+08:00\"\n        \"401\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\n        \"403\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\n        \"404\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotFound\"\n        \"500\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InternalError\"\n  /export/tasks/{taskId}/download:\n    get:\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\n      summary: Download exported file\n      description: |\n        The default mode returns a signed URL and file metadata. Stream delivery\n        is represented by application/octet-stream and equivalent metadata headers.\n      operationId: downloadExportTask\n      parameters:\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskId\"\n        - name: mode\n          in: query\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/DeliveryMode\"\n            default: SIGNED_URL\n      responses:\n        \"200\":\n          description: Signed URL response or file stream.\n          headers:\n            X-Export-File-Name:\n              schema:\n                type: string\n            X-Export-File-Size:\n              schema:\n                type: integer\n                format: int64\n            X-Export-Checksum:\n              schema:\n                type: string\n            X-Export-Checksum-Algorithm:\n              schema:\n                type: string\n                enum: [SHA-256]\n            X-Export-Attempt-No:\n              schema:\n                type: integer\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/DownloadResponseEnvelope\"\n              examples:\n                signedUrl:\n                  value:\n                    code: SUCCESS\n                    message: success\n                    data:\n                      deliveryMode: SIGNED_URL\n                      downloadUrl: \"https://oss.example.com/signed-url\"\n                      expiresAt: \"2026-05-13T10:10:00+08:00\"\n                      fileName: purchase-order-export-20260513.zip\n                      fileSize: 1048576\n                      contentType: application/zip\n                      checksum: sha256:file-checksum\n                      checksumAlgorithm: SHA-256\n                      storageKey: exports/purchase/purchase-order-export/20260513/exp_20260513_000001/1/purchase-order-export-20260513.zip\n                      attemptNo: 1\n            application/octet-stream:\n              schema:\n                type: string\n                format: binary\n        \"400\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/FileNotReady\"\n        \"401\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\n        \"403\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\n        \"404\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotFound\"\n        \"410\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/FileExpired\"\n        \"500\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/FileVerifyError\"\n        \"502\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/ExportRenderError\"\n      x-contract-errorResponses:\n        - FILE_NOT_READY\n        - FILE_VERIFY_ERROR\n        - EXPORT_RENDER_ERROR\n        - INTERNAL_ERROR\n  /export/tasks/{taskId}/cancel:\n    post:\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\n      summary: Cancel export task\n      description: |\n        PENDING tasks can be canceled immediately. EXECUTING tasks accept cancel\n        intent and still return EXECUTING until the worker closes the task at a\n        batch boundary. The API never returns an internal cancel marker as a task status.\n      operationId: cancelExportTask\n      parameters:\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskId\"\n      requestBody:\n        required: false\n        content:\n          application/json:\n            schema:\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/TaskActionRequest\"\n      responses:\n        \"200\":\n          description: Cancel accepted or completed.\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/TaskActionResponseEnvelope\"\n        \"400\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InvalidTaskState\"\n        \"401\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\n        \"403\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\n        \"404\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotFound\"\n        \"500\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InternalError\"\n  /export/tasks/{taskId}/retry:\n    post:\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\n      summary: Retry failed export task\n      description: |\n        Only FAILED tasks are retryable. Retry keeps the original taskId,\n        reuses the original config snapshot, increments attemptNo and creates no\n        second active execution attempt.\n      operationId: retryExportTask\n      parameters:\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskId\"\n      requestBody:\n        required: false\n        content:\n          application/json:\n            schema:\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/TaskActionRequest\"\n      responses:\n        \"200\":\n          description: Retry accepted.\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/TaskActionResponseEnvelope\"\n        \"400\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InvalidTaskState\"\n        \"409\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/ActiveAttemptConflict\"\n        \"401\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\n        \"403\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\n        \"404\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotFound\"\n        \"500\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InternalError\"\n  /export/registries:\n    post:\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\n      summary: Create export registry\n      operationId: createExportRegistry\n      parameters:\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\n      requestBody:\n        required: true\n        content:\n          application/json:\n            schema:\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryUpsertRequest\"\n            examples:\n              purchaseOrderRegistry:\n                value:\n                  taskCode: purchase-order-export\n                  subsystemCode: purchase\n                  displayName: Purchase order export\n                  enabled: true\n                  concurrencyLimit: 3\n                  fileRetentionDays: 15\n                  taskHistoryRetentionDays: 30\n                  singleFileMaxRows: 20000\n                  exportMaxRows: 100000\n                  supportedFormats: [XLSX, ZIP]\n                  datasourceCode: purchase_ro\n                  parameterSchema:\n                    required: [createdAtFrom, createdAtTo]\n                    properties:\n                      createdAtFrom:\n                        type: string\n                        format: date-time\n                      createdAtTo:\n                        type: string\n                        format: date-time\n                      orderStatus:\n                        type: string\n                      supplierId:\n                        type: string\n                      purchaseOrgId:\n                        type: string\n                      keyword:\n                        type: string\n                  queryTemplate:\n                    queryTemplateVersion: v1\n                    templateText: \"select ... where created_at between :createdAtFrom and :createdAtTo order by order_id asc\"\n                    allowedParameters: [createdAtFrom, createdAtTo, orderStatus, supplierId, purchaseOrgId, keyword]\n                  fieldMappings:\n                    - fieldCode: orderNo\n                      headerName: Order No\n                      fieldType: STRING\n                      orderNo: 1\n                      sensitive: false\n                      exportable: true\n                    - fieldCode: contactPhone\n                      headerName: Contact Phone\n                      fieldType: STRING\n                      orderNo: 10\n                      sensitive: true\n                      exportable: true\n                      maskingRuleCode: phone_mask\n                  maskingPolicy:\n                    rules:\n                      phone_mask:\n                        type: PHONE\n                        preservePrefix: 3\n                        preserveSuffix: 4\n                  dataScopeTemplate: \"tenant_id = :tenantId and org_id in (:orgScope)\"\n                  cursorField: orderId\n                  orderBy:\n                    - field: orderId\n                      direction: ASC\n                  batchSize: 1000\n      x-contract-errorResponses:\n        - QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID\n        - FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\n        - MASKING_RULE_ERROR\n        - REGISTRY_CONFLICT\n        - INTERNAL_ERROR\n      responses:\n        \"201\":\n          description: Registry created.\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryEnvelope\"\n        \"400\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/RegistryBadRequest\"\n        \"401\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\n        \"403\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\n        \"409\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/RegistryConflict\"\n        \"500\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/RegistryServerError\"\n    get:\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\n      summary: List export registries\n      operationId: listExportRegistries\n      parameters:\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\n        - name: taskCode\n          in: query\n          schema:\n            type: string\n        - name: subsystemCode\n          in: query\n          schema:\n            type: string\n        - name: enabled\n          in: query\n          schema:\n            type: boolean\n        - name: page\n          in: query\n          schema:\n            type: integer\n            minimum: 1\n            default: 1\n        - name: pageSize\n          in: query\n          schema:\n            type: integer\n            minimum: 1\n            maximum: 100\n            default: 20\n      responses:\n        \"200\":\n          description: Paged registry list.\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryPageEnvelope\"\n        \"401\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\n        \"403\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\n        \"500\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InternalError\"\n  /export/registries/{taskCode}:\n    get:\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\n      summary: Get export registry\n      operationId: getExportRegistry\n      parameters:\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskCode\"\n      responses:\n        \"200\":\n          description: Registry detail.\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryEnvelope\"\n        \"401\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\n        \"403\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\n        \"404\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotRegistered\"\n        \"500\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InternalError\"\n    put:\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\n      summary: Update export registry\n      description: Registry updates only affect tasks created after the update.\n      operationId: updateExportRegistry\n      parameters:\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskCode\"\n      requestBody:\n        required: true\n        content:\n          application/json:\n            schema:\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryUpsertRequest\"\n      x-contract-errorResponses:\n        - QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID\n        - FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\n        - MASKING_RULE_ERROR\n        - INTERNAL_ERROR\n      responses:\n        \"200\":\n          description: Registry updated.\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryEnvelope\"\n        \"400\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/RegistryBadRequest\"\n        \"401\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\n        \"403\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\n        \"404\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotRegistered\"\n        \"500\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/RegistryServerError\"\n  /export/registries/{taskCode}/enable:\n    post:\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\n      summary: Enable export registry\n      operationId: enableExportRegistry\n      parameters:\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskCode\"\n      responses:\n        \"200\":\n          description: Registry enabled.\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryEnvelope\"\n        \"401\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\n        \"403\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\n        \"404\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotRegistered\"\n        \"500\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InternalError\"\n  /export/registries/{taskCode}/disable:\n    post:\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\n      summary: Disable export registry\n      operationId: disableExportRegistry\n      parameters:\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskCode\"\n      responses:\n        \"200\":\n          description: Registry disabled.\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryEnvelope\"\n        \"401\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\n        \"403\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\n        \"404\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotRegistered\"\n        \"500\":\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InternalError\"\ncomponents:\n  securitySchemes:\n    OperatorId:\n      type: apiKey\n      in: header\n      name: X-Operator-Id\n      description: Authenticated operator id forwarded by gateway or caller.\n    TenantId:\n      type: apiKey\n      in: header\n      name: X-Tenant-Id\n      description: Tenant id forwarded by gateway or caller.\n    RoleCodes:\n      type: apiKey\n      in: header\n      name: X-Role-Codes\n      description: Comma-separated role codes forwarded by gateway or caller.\n    OrgScope:\n      type: apiKey\n      in: header\n      name: X-Org-Scope\n      description: Organization scope forwarded by gateway or caller.\n    RequestId:\n      type: apiKey\n      in: header\n      name: X-Request-Id\n      description: Request id used by audit logs and task events.\n  parameters:\n    XOperatorId:\n      name: X-Operator-Id\n      in: header\n      required: true\n      schema:\n        type: string\n      description: Authenticated operator id.\n    XTenantId:\n      name: X-Tenant-Id\n      in: header\n      required: true\n      schema:\n        type: string\n      description: Tenant id for task visibility and data scope.\n    XRoleCodes:\n      name: X-Role-Codes\n      in: header\n      required: true\n      schema:\n        type: string\n      description: Comma-separated role codes.\n    XOrgScope:\n      name: X-Org-Scope\n      in: header\n      required: true\n      schema:\n        type: string\n      description: Organization scope expression or encoded scope list.\n    XRequestId:\n      name: X-Request-Id\n      in: header\n      required: true\n      schema:\n        type: string\n      description: Upstream request id used by audit logs and task events.\n    TaskId:\n      name: taskId\n      in: path\n      required: true\n      schema:\n        type: string\n    TaskCode:\n      name: taskCode\n      in: path\n      required: true\n      schema:\n        type: string\n  responses:\n    AuthContextMissing:\n      description: Required auth context is missing or malformed.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            authMissing:\n              value:\n                code: AUTH_CONTEXT_MISSING\n                message: auth context missing\n                data: null\n    PermissionDenied:\n      description: Operator has no permission for the task, registry or file.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            denied:\n              value:\n                code: PERMISSION_DENIED\n                message: permission denied\n                data: null\n    TaskNotFound:\n      description: Task not found or invisible to current operator.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            notFound:\n              value:\n                code: TASK_NOT_FOUND\n                message: task not found\n                data: null\n    TaskNotRegistered:\n      description: taskCode is not registered.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            notRegistered:\n              value:\n                code: TASK_NOT_REGISTERED\n                message: task code not registered\n                data: null\n    CreateTaskBadRequest:\n      description: Create task request is invalid, disabled or exceeds configured limits.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            validation:\n              value:\n                code: VALIDATION_ERROR\n                message: validation failed\n                data: null\n                errors:\n                  - field: taskCode\n                    reason: required\n            taskDisabled:\n              value:\n                code: TASK_DISABLED\n                message: task code is disabled\n                data:\n                  taskCode: purchase-order-export\n            queryParamsTooLarge:\n              value:\n                code: QUERY_PARAMS_TOO_LARGE\n                message: queryParams exceeds 32768 bytes\n                data: null\n            exportLimitExceeded:\n              value:\n                code: EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED\n                message: export limit exceeded\n                data:\n                  exportMaxRows: 100000\n    IdempotencyConflict:\n      description: Same idempotency scope with different request digest.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            conflict:\n              value:\n                code: IDEMPOTENCY_CONFLICT\n                message: clientRequestId conflicts with a different request digest\n                data:\n                  idempotencyScope: tenant-001:u001:purchase-order-export:req-20260513-0001\n    InvalidTaskState:\n      description: Operation is not allowed for current official task status.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            invalidRetry:\n              value:\n                code: INVALID_TASK_STATE\n                message: current task status does not allow this operation\n                data:\n                  status: EXECUTING\n    ActiveAttemptConflict:\n      description: Another active execution attempt already exists.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            activeAttempt:\n              value:\n                code: ACTIVE_ATTEMPT_CONFLICT\n                message: active execution attempt already exists\n                data:\n                  taskId: exp_20260513_000001\n                  attemptNo: 1\n    FileExpired:\n      description: File is expired or marked as not downloadable.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            expired:\n              value:\n                code: FILE_EXPIRED\n                message: file expired\n                data: null\n    FileNotReady:\n      description: File is not published or the task is not completed yet.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            notReady:\n              value:\n                code: FILE_NOT_READY\n                message: file is not ready for download\n                data:\n                  status: EXECUTING\n    FileVerifyError:\n      description: File upload, metadata or checksum verification failed before publish.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            verifyFailed:\n              value:\n                code: FILE_VERIFY_ERROR\n                message: file verification failed\n                data:\n                  checksumAlgorithm: SHA-256\n    DatasourceUnavailable:\n      description: Datasource or datasource credential is unavailable.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            datasourceUnavailable:\n              value:\n                code: DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE\n                message: datasource unavailable\n                data:\n                  datasourceCode: purchase_ro\n    QueryExecutionError:\n      description: Query execution failed, batch retries exhausted or cursor contract violated.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            queryFailed:\n              value:\n                code: QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR\n                message: query execution failed\n                data:\n                  cursorField: orderId\n    RegistryBadRequest:\n      description: Registry request is invalid, exceeds limits, or contains invalid field/masking configuration.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            validation:\n              value:\n                code: VALIDATION_ERROR\n                message: validation failed\n                data: null\n            exportLimitExceeded:\n              value:\n                code: EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED\n                message: export limit exceeded\n                data:\n                  exportMaxRows: 100000\n            fieldMappingInvalid:\n              value:\n                code: FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\n                message: field mapping invalid\n                data:\n                  fieldCode: contactPhone\n            maskingRuleError:\n              value:\n                code: MASKING_RULE_ERROR\n                message: masking rule error\n                data:\n                  maskingRuleCode: phone_mask\n    RegistryServerError:\n      description: Registry contract references an invalid query template, datasource, field mapping or masking backend.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            queryTemplateInvalid:\n              value:\n                code: QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID\n                message: query template invalid\n                data:\n                  taskCode: purchase-order-export\n            datasourceUnavailable:\n              value:\n                code: DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE\n                message: datasource unavailable\n                data:\n                  datasourceCode: purchase_ro\n            fieldMappingInvalid:\n              value:\n                code: FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\n                message: field mapping invalid\n                data:\n                  fieldCode: contactPhone\n            maskingRuleError:\n              value:\n                code: MASKING_RULE_ERROR\n                message: masking rule error\n                data:\n                  maskingRuleCode: phone_mask\n    ExportRenderError:\n      description: XLSX or ZIP render failed.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            renderFailed:\n              value:\n                code: EXPORT_RENDER_ERROR\n                message: export render error\n                data:\n                  fileFormat: ZIP\n    RegistryConflict:\n      description: Registry taskCode already exists or conflicts with immutable fields.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            duplicate:\n              value:\n                code: REGISTRY_CONFLICT\n                message: taskCode already exists\n                data: null\n    InternalError:\n      description: Unclassified server-side error. Specific platform errors should use a more precise response when known.\n      content:\n        application/json:\n          schema:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\n          examples:\n            internalError:\n              value:\n                code: INTERNAL_ERROR\n                message: internal error\n                data: null\n  schemas:\n    ResponseCode:\n      type: string\n      enum:\n        - SUCCESS\n        - VALIDATION_ERROR\n        - AUTH_CONTEXT_MISSING\n        - PERMISSION_DENIED\n        - TASK_NOT_FOUND\n        - TASK_NOT_REGISTERED\n        - TASK_DISABLED\n        - QUERY_PARAMS_TOO_LARGE\n        - IDEMPOTENCY_CONFLICT\n        - INVALID_TASK_STATE\n        - FILE_EXPIRED\n        - FILE_NOT_READY\n        - FILE_VERIFY_ERROR\n        - QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID\n        - DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE\n        - QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR\n        - FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\n        - MASKING_RULE_ERROR\n        - EXPORT_RENDER_ERROR\n        - EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED\n        - REGISTRY_CONFLICT\n        - ACTIVE_ATTEMPT_CONFLICT\n        - INTERNAL_ERROR\n    TaskStatus:\n      type: string\n      description: Official public task status. Internal cancel flags are not valid values.\n      enum: [PENDING, EXECUTING, COMPLETED, FAILED, CANCELED, EXPIRED]\n    FileFormat:\n      type: string\n      enum: [XLSX, ZIP]\n    DeliveryMode:\n      type: string\n      enum: [SIGNED_URL, STREAM]\n    Envelope:\n      type: object\n      required: [code, message]\n      properties:\n        code:\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ResponseCode\"\n        message:\n          type: string\n    ErrorEnvelope:\n      allOf:\n        - $ref: \"#/components/schemas/Envelope\"\n        - type: object\n          properties:\n            data:\n              type: object\n              nullable: true\n              additionalProperties: true\n            errors:\n              type: array\n              items:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/FieldError\"\n    FieldError:\n      type: object\n      required: [field, reason]\n      properties:\n        field:\n          type: string\n        reason:\n          type: string\n    CreateExportTaskRequest:\n      type: object\n      required: [taskCode, subsystemCode, fileFormat, queryParams]\n      properties:\n        taskCode:\n          type: string\n        subsystemCode:\n          type: string\n        fileFormat:\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/FileFormat\"\n        clientRequestId:\n          type: string\n          maxLength: 128\n          description: Optional idempotency key scoped by tenantId/operatorId/taskCode.\n        queryParams:\n          type: object\n          additionalProperties: true\n          description: Must match registry parameter schema and must not exceed 32768 bytes after canonical JSON serialization.\n        deliveryPreference:\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/DeliveryMode\"\n    CreateExportTaskResponseEnvelope:\n      allOf:\n        - $ref: \"#/components/schemas/Envelope\"\n        - type: object\n          required: [data]\n          properties:\n            data:\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/CreateExportTaskResponse\"\n    CreateExportTaskResponse:\n      type: object\n      required:\n        - taskId\n        - taskCode\n        - subsystemCode\n        - status\n        - idempotencyScope\n        - requestDigest\n        - configSnapshotDigest\n        - attemptNo\n        - createdAt\n      properties:\n        taskId:\n          type: string\n        taskCode:\n          type: string\n        subsystemCode:\n          type: string\n        status:\n          type: string\n          enum: [PENDING]\n        clientRequestId:\n          type: string\n        idempotencyHit:\n          type: boolean\n        idempotencyScope:\n          type: string\n          description: Stable success-response evidence for the tenantId + operatorId + taskCode + clientRequestId idempotency scope.\n        requestDigest:\n          type: string\n        configSnapshotDigest:\n          type: string\n        attemptNo:\n          type: integer\n          minimum: 0\n        createdAt:\n          type: string\n          format: date-time\n    ExportTaskDetailEnvelope:\n      allOf:\n        - $ref: \"#/components/schemas/Envelope\"\n        - type: object\n          required: [data]\n          properties:\n            data:\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportTaskDetail\"\n    ExportTaskDetail:\n      type: object\n      required:\n        - taskId\n        - taskCode\n        - subsystemCode\n        - status\n        - totalCount\n        - processedCount\n        - progressPercent\n        - attemptNo\n        - requestId\n        - requestDigest\n        - configSnapshotDigest\n        - createdBy\n        - createdAt\n        - updatedAt\n      properties:\n        taskId:\n          type: string\n        taskCode:\n          type: string\n        subsystemCode:\n          type: string\n        status:\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/TaskStatus\"\n        totalCount:\n          type: integer\n          format: int64\n          minimum: 0\n        processedCount:\n          type: integer\n          format: int64\n          minimum: 0\n        progressPercent:\n          type: number\n          minimum: 0\n          maximum: 100\n        fileFormat:\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/FileFormat\"\n        attemptNo:\n          type: integer\n          minimum: 0\n        errorCode:\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ResponseCode\"\n        errorMessage:\n          type: string\n        failureStage:\n          type: string\n        lastSuccessStage:\n          type: string\n        requestId:\n          type: string\n        requestDigest:\n          type: string\n        configSnapshotDigest:\n          type: string\n        createdBy:\n          type: string\n        createdAt:\n          type: string\n          format: date-time\n        updatedAt:\n          type: string\n          format: date-time\n        file:\n          $ref