路径 | `docs/context/architecture-brief.md`、`plans/features/export-platform.dev-plan.md`、`scripts/arch-check.ts`、`npm run arch:check` |\r\n| 备注 | `npm run arch:check` 不能被 `git diff --check`、OpenAPI lint、单测或人工检查替代 |\r\n\r\n## 最终规则\r\n\r\n- `feature_impl` 任务不得只以文档、OpenAPI、内存 repository、mock 或 `git diff --check` 作为完成证据。\r\n- 每个实现任务必须从 `docs/architecture/constraints.md` 复制 `architecture_constraints` 和 `forbidden_implementations`。\r\n- 没有真实依赖时必须记录 `BLOCKED - 需要人工介入`，不得用测试替身绕过。\r\n- `STACK-ADR-001` 当前仍是 design / planned 基线；后续 `feature_impl` 不得只靠文档和 `git diff --check` 通过，必须先具备 `npm run arch:check` 所需的入口、路由映射和 migration 证据。\r\n\nwarning: in-process app-server event stream lagged; dropped 3 events\n succeeded in 714ms:\n# Requirement Interface Matrix：统一导出平台\r\n\r\n\u003e 用于把需求映射到后端 API、调度能力、状态和证据路径。\r\n\r\n## 1. 需求到能力映射\r\n\r\n| Requirement ID | 需求摘要 | 对应能力 | 状态 | 验收入口 |\r\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\r\n| FR-001 | 创建导出任务 | `POST /api/export/tasks` | PENDING | AC-001 |\r\n| FR-002 | 查询任务详情/进度 | `GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}` | PENDING / EXECUTING / COMPLETED / FAILED | AC-002 |\r\n| FR-003 | 下载导出文件 | `GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/download` | COMPLETED / EXPIRED | AC-003 |\r\n| FR-004 | 查询任务历史 | `GET /api/export/tasks` | default / empty / permission_denied | AC-004 |\r\n| FR-005 | 调度和并发控制 | Scheduler + DB lock | PENDING / EXECUTING | AC-005 |\r\n| FR-006 | 大数据分片导出 | Worker + file service | EXECUTING / COMPLETED | AC-006 |\r\n| FR-007 | 注册导出任务 / 启停 / 配置 | `POST /api/export/registries` + registry/config APIs | default / disabled / permission_denied | AC-007 |\r\n| FR-008 | 集中查询模板契约 | registry/config + datasource/query template | default / invalid_template / datasource_error / query_error | AC-008 |\r\n| FR-009 | 权限、脱敏、签名 | auth + data scope + masking + download guard | permission_denied / masking_error | AC-009 |\r\n| FR-010 | 审计与失败追踪 | audit log + task event log | all | AC-010 |\r\n| FR-011 | 过期清理 | cleanup job | EXPIRED | AC-011 |\r\n| FR-012 | 取消和重试 | cancel/retry API | CANCELED / PENDING / FAILED | AC-012 |\r\n| FR-013 | 幂等、执行尝试、锁租约和配置快照 | create API + Scheduler + task snapshot | default / conflict / processing / error | AC-013 / AC-014 / AC-015 / AC-016 |\r\n| FR-014 | 采购订单导出样板 | purchase-order query template + platform export flow | default / empty / long_content / error | AC-017 / AC-018 / AC-E022 / AC-E023 |\r\n| FR-008/FR-010/FR-013 | 查询执行上下文与追踪 | query executor + task event log | default / error | AC-019 / AC-020 |\r\n| FR-003/FR-006/FR-011 | 文件临时对象、发布和校验 | file service / OSS | default / error / expired | AC-021 / AC-E026 |\r\n\r\n## 2. 反查说明\r\n\r\n- 平台负责任务、调度、下载、审计、注册启停、配置同步、集中查询、字段映射、脱敏、文件生成和清理。\r\n- 子系统只负责调用平台任务接口，传递认证上下文和符合注册参数 schema 的业务查询参数。\r\n- 下载能力默认签名 URL，必要场景支持流式下载；两种模式都必须携带文件元信息。\r\n- `FR-004` 历史查询的正式筛选维度为 `taskCode`、`status`、`createdBy`、`createdAtRange`、`fileFormat`、`subsystemCode`；测试层如已先出现更细筛选项，应标记为分析阶段假设而不是既定事实。\r\n- `FR-008` 查询模板契约由注册配置声明数据源、参数 schema、参数化查询模板、字段映射、脱敏策略、数据范围约束、游标字段、排序规则、批大小、行数阈值、保留期和支持格式。\r\n- `FR-012` 取消与重试边界为：PENDING 可取消，FAILED 可重试，EXECUTING 取消按批次边界收口；PENDING/EXECUTING 重试返回非法状态错误且不得重复派发执行。\r\n- `FR-013` 要求创建幂等、执行尝试、锁租约和配置快照形成同一条审计链路；配置变化不得改变已创建任务的执行口径。\r\n- `FR-014` 是一期样板模块合同，不新增平台特例逻辑；它用于证明标准 registry、集中查询模板、调度、文件、权限、审计和下载链路能被一个业务场景完整验证。\r\n\r\n## 3. 接口证据字段\r\n\r\n| 需求 | 最小证据字段 / 行为 | 说明 |\r\n| --- | --- | --- |\r\n| FR-003 | `downloadUrl`、`expiresAt`、`fileName`、`fileSize` 或等价 stream 元信息 | 用于证明下载保护和文件元信息可追踪 |\r\n| FR-004 | `taskCode`、`status`、`createdBy`、`createdAtRange`、`fileFormat`、`subsystemCode` | 正式历史查询筛选维度 |\r\n| FR-007 | `taskCode` 唯一、`enabled`、并发上限、保留期、单文件行数阈值、最大导出量、支持格式策略 | 注册配置必须能被查询和同步 |\r\n| FR-008 | `datasourceCode`、`queryTemplateVersion`、`parameterSchemaDigest`、`fieldMappingDigest`、`maskingPolicyDigest`、`cursorField` | 用于证明集中查询模板、字段映射和脱敏策略可追溯 |\r\n| FR-009 | `operatorId`、`tenantId`、`roleCodes`、`orgScope`、`requestId`、`dataScopeExpression` | 统一认证上下文和数据范围约束最小字段 |\r\n| FR-010 | `taskId`、`taskCode`、`subsystemCode`、`operatorId`、`action`、`result`、`errorCode`、`requestId`、发生时间 | 审计日志最小字段 |\r\n| FR-012 | `attemptNo` 或等价执行尝试序号、内部取消标记、最终状态 | 用于证明重试不丢审计链路、取消不暴露内部状态 |\r\n| FR-013 | `clientRequestId`、`idempotencyScope`、`requestDigest`、`configSnapshotDigest`、`attemptNo`、`lockOwner`、`lockExpireAt`、`leaseRenewedAt` | 用于证明幂等、防重复执行、配置快照和锁租约行为 |\r\n| FR-006/FR-013 | `cursorField`、`lastCursor`、`processedCount`、`filePartNo`、`batchSize`、`batchRowCount`、`retryCount`、`backoffMs` | 用于证明游标分页、锁接管、批次执行和查询重试证据 |\r\n| FR-014 | `taskCode=purchase-order-export`、`subsystemCode=purchase`、`datasourceCode`、`queryTemplateVersion`、`createdAtRange`、`orderStatus`、`supplierId`、`purchaseOrgId`、`keyword`、字段定义、敏感字段脱敏策略、`cursorField=orderId` | 用于证明采购订单样板集中查询合同可执行 |\r\n| FR-008/FR-010/FR-013 | `taskId`、`attemptNo`、`requestId`、`queryTemplateVersion`、`datasourceCode`、`batchCheckpoint` | 用于证明查询执行上下文和审计串联 |\r\n| FR-003/FR-011 | `tempStorageKey`、`publishedStorageKey`、`checksum`、`checksumVerifiedAt`、`publishedAt`、`deliveryReadyAt` | 用于证明临时对象、发布对象、校验和下载准备状态可追踪 |\r\n\r\n## 4. 错误映射\r\n\r\n| 场景 | 对外状态 | 错误码 | 验收入口 |\r\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\r\n| 查询模板不存在或不合法 | `FAILED` | `QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID` | AC-E011 |\r\n| 数据源不可用或凭证不可用 | `FAILED` | `DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE` | AC-E012 |\r\n| 查询执行失败 | `FAILED` | `QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR` | AC-E013 |\r\n| 查询批次重试耗尽 | `FAILED` | `QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR` | AC-E020 |\r\n| 查询模板或字段映射与任务快照冲突 | `FAILED` | `QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID` 或 `FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID` | AC-E024 |\r\n| 字段映射不合法 | `FAILED` | `FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID` | AC-E014 |\r\n| 批次字段、顺序或脱敏结果不合法 | `FAILED` | `FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID` 或 `MASKING_RULE_ERROR` | AC-E025 |\r\n| 脱敏规则配置或执行失败 | `FAILED` | `MASKING_RULE_ERROR` | AC-E022 |\r\n| 文件渲染失败 | `FAILED` | `EXPORT_RENDER_ERROR` | AC-E027 |\r\n| OSS 上传失败 | `FAILED` | `FILE_VERIFY_ERROR` | AC-E005 |\r\n| 文件发布前校验失败 | `FAILED` | `FILE_VERIFY_ERROR` | AC-E026 |\r\n| 采购订单游标缺失、重复或非递增 | `FAILED` | `QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR` | AC-E023 |\r\n\r\n## 5. 缺口\r\n\r\n| Gap ID | 缺口 | 处理方式 |\r\n| --- | --- | --- |\r\n| GAP-001 | 样板模块字段与表头 | 采购订单导出样板覆盖订单号、订单状态、供应商、采购组织、采购员、创建时间、总金额、币种和脱敏后的联系人信息 |\r\n| GAP-002 | 统一认证上下文字段 | 最小字段锁定为 `operatorId`、`tenantId`、`roleCodes`、`orgScope`、`requestId`；联调只确认字段来源和透传方式 |\r\n| GAP-003 | 查询性能基线 | 采购订单样板以 10 万行导出作为基线证据，记录总耗时、批大小、分片数和查询重试情况 |\r\n| GAP-004 | OSS bucket/path、签名有效期和文件校验值生成方式 | bucket 由环境配置；path 默认 `exports/{subsystemCode}/{taskCode}/{yyyyMMdd}/{taskId}/{attemptNo}/{fileName}`；签名 URL 默认 10 分钟；校验默认 `SHA-256` |\r\n| GAP-005 | 采购订单样板合同是否足够驱动实现和测试 | 已锁定 taskCode、subsystemCode、查询条件、字段顺序、敏感字段、游标字段、边界数据和压测证据 |\r\n\n succeeded in 859ms:\n# Contracts 目录约定：统一导出平台\r\n\r\n**Feature ID**: `FEAT-EXPORT-PLATFORM-001`\r\n**最后更新**: 2026-05-14\r\n\r\n## 1. 目录目标\r\n\r\n`contracts/` 是统一导出平台的契约入口目录。这里先固定 API、scheduler、query、file、audit 和 sample 的契约边界，再进入实现与测试。\r\n\r\n## 2. 目录结构\r\n\r\n```text\r\ncontracts/\r\n  README.md\r\n  openapi.yaml\r\n  api/\r\n  scheduler/\r\n  query/\r\n  file/\r\n  audit/\r\n  sample/\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 3. 契约分区\r\n\r\n| 目录 | 约定内容 | 覆盖需求 |\r\n| --- | --- | --- |\r\n| `contracts/api/` | 创建、查询详情、查询历史、下载、取消、重试、注册启停接口 | FR-001, FR-002, FR-004, FR-007, FR-012, FR-013 |\r\n| `contracts/scheduler/` | DB 抢锁、租约、续租、接管、并发控制、批次检查点 | FR-005, FR-013 |\r\n| `contracts/query/` | 参数 schema、查询模板、字段映射、脱敏策略、数据范围、游标分页 | FR-006, FR-008, FR-009, FR-014 |\r\n| `contracts/file/` | 临时对象、发布对象、checksum、下载元信息、清理前置标记 | FR-003, FR-006, FR-011 |\r\n| `contracts/audit/` | 创建、调度、执行、下载、取消、重试、清理审计事件 | FR-010, FR-013 |\r\n| `contracts/sample/` | 采购订单样板查询条件、字段顺序、脱敏和压测证据 | FR-014 |\r\n\r\n## 3.1 ARCH-001 架构锚点\r\n\r\n后续契约文件必须和 `docs/context/architecture-brief.md` 的统一架构决策保持一致，尤其是以下跨模块术语和证据字段：\r\n\r\n| 架构锚点 | 必须进入的契约分区 | 最小字段 / 行为 |\r\n| --- | --- | --- |\r\n| 创建幂等 | `contracts/api/` | `clientRequestId`、成功响应 `idempotencyScope=tenantId+operatorId+taskCode+clientRequestId`、`requestDigest`、`IDEMPOTENCY_CONFLICT` |\r\n| 配置快照 | `contracts/api/`、`contracts/query/` | `configSnapshotDigest`、`datasourceCode`、`queryTemplateVersion`、`parameterSchemaDigest`、`fieldMappingDigest`、`maskingPolicyDigest` |\r\n| DB 抢锁 | `contracts/scheduler/` | `lockOwner`、`lockExpireAt`、`leaseRenewedAt`、数据库时间、5 分钟默认租约 |\r\n| 执行尝试 | `contracts/api/`、`contracts/scheduler/`、`contracts/audit/` | `attemptNo`、FAILED 重试递增、锁接管不递增、同任务同一时刻一个活跃尝试 |\r\n| 批次检查点 | `contracts/scheduler/`、`contracts/query/` | `lastCursor`、`processedCount`、`filePartNo`、`attemptNo`、`retryCount`、`backoffMs` |\r\n| 认证上下文 | `contracts/api/`、`contracts/query/` | `operatorId`、`tenantId`、`roleCodes`、`orgScope`、`requestId`，并叠加数据范围约束 |\r\n| 文件发布 | `contracts/file/` | `tempStorageKey`、`publishedStorageKey`、`checksum`、`checksumAlgorithm`、`checksumVerifiedAt`、`publishedAt`、`deliveryReadyAt` |\r\n| 清理顺序 | `contracts/file/` | 先标记不可下载，再删除对象；失败保留可重试记录 |\r\n| 审计链路 | `contracts/audit/` | `taskId`、`taskCode`、`subsystemCode`、`operatorId`、`action`、`result`、`errorCode`、`requestId`、发生时间 |\r\n| 采购订单样板 | `contracts/sample/`、`contracts/query/`、`contracts/file/` | `taskCode=purchase-order-export`、`subsystemCode=purchase`、`cursorField=orderId`、敏感字段脱敏、`0/1/20000/20001/100000/100001` 行边界 |\r\n\r\n## 3.2 后续 owned paths 依据\r\n\r\n`contracts/README.md` 是当前已存在的契约入口。后续任务创建新文件时，应按能力分区声明 owned paths：\r\n\r\n- 对外 API：`contracts/openapi.yaml`、`contracts/api/`\r\n- 调度锁与执行尝试：`contracts/scheduler/`\r\n- 集中查询、参数 schema、字段映射和脱敏：`contracts/query/`\r\n- 文件临时对象、发布、下载和清理前置标记：`contracts/file/`\r\n- 审计动作和阶段事件：`contracts/audit/`\r\n- 采购订单样板合同：`contracts/sample/`\r\n\r\n实现层和测试层的真实路径由 `plans/features/export-platform.dev-plan.md` 继续约束：契约先行，其次 `tests/contract/`、`tests/backend/`、`tests/scheduler/`、`tests/query/`、`tests/file/`、`tests/sample/`，最后才创建对应 `src/*` 模块。\r\n\r\n## 3.3 CONTRACT-001 已落地契约\r\n\r\n`contracts/openapi.yaml` 是当前统一导出平台的对外 API 和错误码锚点，覆盖 `FR-001`、`FR-002`、`FR-003`、`FR-004`、`FR-007`、`FR-008`、`FR-009`、`FR-010`、`FR-012`、`FR-013`。\r\n\r\n| 接口 | 方法 | 覆盖需求 | 关键契约 |\r\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\r\n| `/api/export/tasks` | `POST` | FR-001 / FR-009 / FR-013 | 创建任务、最小认证上下文、`clientRequestId` 幂等、成功响应 `idempotencyScope`、`requestDigest`、`configSnapshotDigest` |\r\n| `/api/export/tasks` | `GET` | FR-004 / FR-009 / FR-010 | 正式筛选维度、普通用户仅本人、管理员按权限全局查询 |\r\n| `/api/export/tasks/{taskId}` | `GET` | FR-002 / FR-010 | 详情、进度、失败错误码、批次检查点和文件元信息 |\r\n| `/api/export/tasks/{taskId}/download` | `GET` | FR-003 / FR-009 / FR-010 | 签名 URL、stream 元信息、文件校验、过期与权限失败 |\r\n| `/api/export/tasks/{taskId}/cancel` | `POST` | FR-012 / FR-010 | PENDING 取消、EXECUTING 批次边界取消；不暴露内部取消状态 |\r\n| `/api/export/tasks/{taskId}/retry` | `POST` | FR-012 / FR-013 / FR-010 | 仅 FAILED 可重试，沿用 `taskId` 和配置快照，递增 `attemptNo` |\r\n| `/api/export/registries` | `POST` / `GET` | FR-007 / FR-008 / FR-009 | 注册创建、查询、并发、保留期、阈值、格式、查询模板和字段映射 |\r\n| `/api/export/registries/{taskCode}` | `GET` / `PUT` | FR-007 / FR-008 / FR-013 | 配置详情、更新与新任务快照口径 |\r\n| `/api/export/registries/{taskCode}/enable` | `POST` | FR-007 | 启用注册配置 |\r\n| `/api/export/registries/{taskCode}/disable` | `POST` | FR-007 | 禁用注册配置，创建阶段返回 `TASK_DISABLED` |\r\n\r\n## 3.4 对外状态和错误码\r\n\r\n对外任务状态只能使用 `PENDING`、`EXECUTING`、`COMPLETED`、`FAILED`、`CANCELED`、`EXPIRED`。执行中取消意图只能通过动作响应字段表达，不得作为任务状态返回。\r\n\r\n| 错误码 | 默认 HTTP 状态 | 场景 |\r\n| --- | --- | --- |\r\n| `VALIDATION_ERROR` | 400 | 参数校验失败 |\r\n| `AUTH_CONTEXT_MISSING` | 401 | 缺少 `operatorId`、`tenantId`、`roleCodes`、`orgScope` 或 `requestId` |\r\n| `PERMISSION_DENIED` | 403 | 创建、查询、下载或配置操作无权限 |\r\n| `TASK_NOT_FOUND` | 404 | 任务不存在或对当前用户不可见 |\r\n| `TASK_NOT_REGISTERED` | 404 | `taskCode` 未注册 |\r\n| `TASK_DISABLED` | 400 | `taskCode` 已禁用 |\r\n| `QUERY_PARAMS_TOO_LARGE` | 400 | `queryParams` 超过 32KB 默认限制 |\r\n| `IDEMPOTENCY_CONFLICT` | 409 | 相同幂等范围但参数摘要不同 |\r\n| `INVALID_TASK_STATE` | 400 | 当前状态不允许下载、取消或重试 |\r\n| `ACTIVE_ATTEMPT_CONFLICT` | 409 | 已存在活跃执行尝试 |\r\n| `FILE_EXPIRED` | 410 | 文件已过期或已标记不可下载 |\r\n| `FILE_NOT_READY` | 400 | 文件未发布或任务尚未完成 |\r\n| `FILE_VERIFY_ERROR` | 500 | OSS 上传、元信息或校验失败 |\r\n| `QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID` | 500 | 查询模板不存在、不合法或与快照冲突 |\r\n| `DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE` | 500 | 数据源或凭证不可用 |\r\n| `QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR` | 500 | 查询执行失败、批次重试耗尽或游标异常 |\r\n| `FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID` | 500 | 字段映射、字段顺序或字段白名单不合法 |\r\n| `MASKING_RULE_ERROR` | 500 | 脱敏策略配置或执行失败 |\r\n| `EXPORT_RENDER_ERROR` | 500 | XLSX/ZIP 渲染失败 |\r\n| `EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED` | 400 | 超过默认或配置化最大导出量 |\r\n| `REGISTRY_CONFLICT` | 409 | 注册 `taskCode` 冲突 |\r\n| `INTERNAL_ERROR` | 500 | 未分类服务端错误 |\r\n\r\n## 3.5 CONTRACT-REVIEW-001 生产边界追踪要求\r\n\r\n`contracts/openapi.yaml` 通过 `x-contract-implementation-trace` 固化每个公开 operation 的后续实现追踪要求。该扩展只声明后续生产路径义务，不作为实现已完成证据。\r\n\r\n| operationId | HTTP 入口 | Requirement IDs | 后续 handler | DB / worker / audit / file 追踪要求 | 后续测试映射 |\r\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\r\n| `createExportTask` | `POST /api/export/tasks` | FR-001 / FR-009 / FR-013 | `src/routes/export/tasks/create-export-task.handler.ts` | DB: task、idempotency、registry、audit；worker: 消费已提交 `PENDING`；audit: `CREATE` | contract / api / db |\r\n| `listExportTasks` | `GET /api/export/tasks` | FR-004 / FR-009 / FR-010 | `src/routes/export/tasks/list-export-tasks.handler.ts` | DB: task、file、audit；audit: `QUERY_HISTORY`；file: 只返回已发布文件元信息 | contract / api |\r\n| `getExportTask` | `GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}` | FR-002 / FR-010 / FR-013 | `src/routes/export/tasks/get-export-task.handler.ts` | DB: task、event、attempt、file；worker: checkpoint / lease 证据；audit: `DETAIL_VIEW` | contract / api |\r\n| `downloadExportTask` | `GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/download` | FR-003 / FR-009 / FR-010 | `src/routes/export/tasks/download-export-task.handler.ts` | DB: task、file、audit；file: published object、checksum、expiry、delivery mode；audit: `DOWNLOAD` | contract / file |\r\n| `cancelExportTask` | `POST /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/cancel` | FR-012 / FR-010 | `src/routes/export/tasks/cancel-export-task.handler.ts` | DB: task、event、audit；worker: EXECUTING 批次边界收口；audit: cancel request/done | contract / worker |\r\n| `retryExportTask` | `POST /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/retry` | FR-012 / FR-013 / FR-010 | `src/routes/export/tasks/retry-export-task.handler.ts` | DB: task、attempt、event、audit；worker: 仅 FAILED 入队新尝试；audit: retry request | contract / db |\r\n| `createExportRegistry` | `POST /api/export/registries` | FR-007 / FR-008 / FR-009 | `src/routes/export/registries/create-export-registry.handler.ts` | DB: registry、registry version、audit；query: schema/template/mapping/masking snapshot；audit: `REGISTRY_CREATE` | contract / api |\r\n| `listExportRegistries` | `GET /api/export/registries` | FR-007 / FR-008 / FR-009 | `src/routes/export/registries/list-export-registries.handler.ts` | DB: registry、registry version；audit: `REGISTRY_QUERY` | contract |\r\n| `getExportRegistry` | `GET /api/export/registries/{taskCode}` | FR-007 / FR-008 / FR-013 | `src/routes/export/registries/get-export-registry.handler.ts` | DB: registry、registry version；snapshot digest 必须可追溯；audit: `REGISTRY_DETAIL` | contract |\r\n| `updateExportRegistry` | `PUT /api/export/registries/{taskCode}` | FR-007 / FR-008 / FR-013 | `src/routes/export/registries/update-export-registry.handler.ts` | DB: registry、registry version、audit；worker/query: 更新只影响新任务，旧任务继续使用快照；audit: `REGISTRY_UPDATE` | contract / db |\r\n| `enableExportRegistry` | `POST /api/export/registries/{taskCode}/enable` | FR-007 | `src/routes/export/registries/enable-export-registry.handler.ts` | DB: registry、audit；audit: `REGISTRY_ENABLE` | contract |\r\n| `disableExportRegistry` | `POST /api/export/registries/{taskCode}/disable` | FR-007 | `src/routes/export/registries/disable-export-registry.handler.ts` | DB: registry、audit；后续创建必须返回 `TASK_DISABLED`；audit: `REGISTRY_DISABLE` | contract |\r\n\r\n后续 HTTP handler 实现任务必须从该表和 `openapi.yaml` 扩展生成 route / handler / test TODO，且不得把 OpenAPI 契约、Markdown 表格或 `git diff --check` 作为 production path 完成证据。\r\n\r\n## 4. 契约编写规则\r\n\r\n1. `openapi.yaml` 只放对外 API 的正式入口和状态/错误码锚点。\r\n2. 分区目录里的契约文件按能力拆分，不把所有场景塞进单个大文件。\r\n3. 每个契约必须能回指到至少一个 Requirement ID 和一个验收入口。\r\n4. API 契约、scheduler 契约、query 契约、file 契约、audit 契约和 sample 契约必须保持同一组术语，尤其是 `attemptNo`、`configSnapshotDigest`、`batchCheckpoint`、`storageKey`、`requestId`。\r\n5. 文件发布契约必须明确临时对象和已发布对象的边界，避免下载接口误暴露未发布对象。\r\n6. query 契约必须明确禁止原始 SQL，只允许参数化模板和参数 schema 绑定。\r\n7. scheduler 契约必须明确数据库时间、锁租约和接管规则，不允许依赖本机时间。\r\n\r\n## 5. 文件命名建议\r\n\r\n| 类型 | 命名建议 | 示例 |\r\n| --- | --- | --- |\r\n| API 契约 | `*.openapi.yaml` 或 `*.md` | `contracts/api/export-tasks.openapi.yaml` |\r\n| Scheduler 契约 | `*.md` | `contracts/scheduler/lease-and-lock.md` |\r\n| Query 契约 | `*.md` 或 `*.schema.json` | `contracts/query/template-and-mapping.md` |\r\n| File 契约 | `*.md` | `contracts/file/publish-and-download.md` |\r\n| Audit 契约 | `*.md` | `contracts/audit/task-events.md` |\r\n| Sample 契约 | `*.md` | `contracts/sample/purchase-order-export.md` |\r\n\r\n## 6. 使用顺序\r\n\r\n1. 先补 `contracts/openapi.yaml`，锚定对外 API。\r\n2. 再按 `api/`、`scheduler/`、`query/`、`file/`、`audit/`、`sample/` 分区补齐契约说明。\r\n3. 契约定稿后，测试目录按同名能力分区创建，保证测试层和契约层可一一对应。\r\n\r\n## 6.1 验证入口\r\n\r\n当前任务的最小验证命令为：\r\n\r\n```powershell\r\ngit diff --check -- contracts docs/testing/verify-matrix.md\r\nnpx --yes @redocly/cli@1.34.5 lint contracts/openapi.yaml\r\n```\r\n\r\n后续创建 Node 或契约测试工程后，应把 OpenAPI 校验固化为 package script，例如：\r\n\r\n```powershell\r\npowershell -NoProfile -Command \"npm run test:contract\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 7. 约束\r\n\r\n- 不在 `contracts/` 里写实现代码。\r\n- 不用 `contracts/` 替代 `docs/testing/` 的追溯矩阵和验证矩阵。\r\n- 不把样板契约写成平台特例接口，样板必须复用标准平台契约。\r\n\n succeeded in 1037ms:\nopenapi: 3.0.3\r\ninfo:\r\n  title: Export Platform API Contract\r\n  version: 1.0.0\r\n  license:\r\n    name: Internal\r\n    url: https://example.invalid/internal-license\r\n  description: |\r\n    CONTRACT-001 defines the public API contract for FEAT-EXPORT-PLATFORM-001.\r\n    The API consumes authentication context from upstream services and exposes\r\n    only official task statuses: PENDING, EXECUTING, COMPLETED, FAILED,\r\n    CANCELED, EXPIRED.\r\nservers:\r\n  - url: /api\r\n    description: Relative platform API base path\r\ntags:\r\n  - name: ExportTasks\r\n    description: Task creation, detail, history, download, cancel and retry APIs.\r\n  - name: ExportRegistries\r\n    description: Export task registry, enable/disable and configuration APIs.\r\nsecurity:\r\n  - OperatorId: []\r\n    TenantId: []\r\n    RoleCodes: []\r\n    OrgScope: []\r\n    RequestId: []\r\nx-contract-implementation-trace:\r\n  description: |\r\n    CONTRACT-REVIEW-001 requires every public operation to stay traceable to\r\n    later HTTP handler, persistence, worker, audit, file and test obligations.\r\n    Paths below are planned implementation targets, not current implementation evidence.\r\n  operations:\r\n    createExportTask:\r\n      http: POST /api/export/tasks\r\n      requirements: [FR-001, FR-009, FR-013]\r\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-001, AE-009, AE-014]\r\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/create-export-task.handler.ts\r\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_idempotency, export_registries, export_audit_logs]\r\n      worker: [scheduler must consume committed PENDING task]\r\n      audit: [CREATE]\r\n      file: []\r\n      tests:\r\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.create.contract.test.ts\r\n        - tests/api/export-tasks.create.api.test.ts\r\n        - tests/db/export-task-idempotency.repository.test.ts\r\n    listExportTasks:\r\n      http: GET /api/export/tasks\r\n      requirements: [FR-004, FR-009, FR-010]\r\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-004, AE-009, AE-010]\r\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/list-export-tasks.handler.ts\r\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_files, export_audit_logs]\r\n      worker: []\r\n      audit: [QUERY_HISTORY]\r\n      file: []\r\n      tests:\r\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.list.contract.test.ts\r\n        - tests/api/export-tasks.visibility.api.test.ts\r\n    getExportTask:\r\n      http: GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}\r\n      requirements: [FR-002, FR-010, FR-013]\r\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-002, AE-010, AE-013]\r\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/get-export-task.handler.ts\r\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_events, export_task_attempts, export_task_files]\r\n      worker: [batch checkpoint and lease fields are worker-produced evidence]\r\n      audit: [DETAIL_VIEW]\r\n      file: [file metadata must exclude unpublished objects]\r\n      tests:\r\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.detail.contract.test.ts\r\n        - tests/api/export-tasks.detail.api.test.ts\r\n    downloadExportTask:\r\n      http: GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/download\r\n      requirements: [FR-003, FR-009, FR-010]\r\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-003, AE-009, AE-021]\r\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/download-export-task.handler.ts\r\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_files, export_audit_logs]\r\n      worker: []\r\n      audit: [DOWNLOAD]\r\n      file: [file service must validate published object, checksum, expiry and delivery mode]\r\n      tests:\r\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.download.contract.test.ts\r\n        - tests/file/export-file-download.guard.test.ts\r\n    cancelExportTask:\r\n      http: POST /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/cancel\r\n      requirements: [FR-012, FR-010]\r\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-012]\r\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/cancel-export-task.handler.ts\r\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_events, export_audit_logs]\r\n      worker: [EXECUTING cancel closes at a persisted batch boundary]\r\n      audit: [CANCEL_REQUEST, CANCEL_DONE]\r\n      file: []\r\n      tests:\r\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.cancel.contract.test.ts\r\n        - tests/worker/export-task-cancel-boundary.test.ts\r\n    retryExportTask:\r\n      http: POST /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/retry\r\n      requirements: [FR-012, FR-013, FR-010]\r\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-012, AE-013]\r\n      handler: src/routes/export/tasks/retry-export-task.handler.ts\r\n      db: [export_tasks, export_task_attempts, export_task_events, export_audit_logs]\r\n      worker: [retry enqueues a new attempt only for FAILED tasks]\r\n      audit: [RETRY_REQUEST]\r\n      file: []\r\n      tests:\r\n        - tests/contract/export-tasks.retry.contract.test.ts\r\n        - tests/db/export-task-attempt.repository.test.ts\r\n    createExportRegistry:\r\n      http: POST /api/export/registries\r\n      requirements: [FR-007, FR-008, FR-009]\r\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007, AE-008, AE-016]\r\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/create-export-registry.handler.ts\r\n      db: [export_registries, export_registry_versions, export_audit_logs]\r\n      worker: []\r\n      audit: [REGISTRY_CREATE]\r\n      file: []\r\n      tests:\r\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.create.contract.test.ts\r\n        - tests/api/export-registries.create.api.test.ts\r\n    listExportRegistries:\r\n      http: GET /api/export/registries\r\n      requirements: [FR-007, FR-008, FR-009]\r\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007, AE-008]\r\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/list-export-registries.handler.ts\r\n      db: [export_registries, export_registry_versions]\r\n      worker: []\r\n      audit: [REGISTRY_QUERY]\r\n      file: []\r\n      tests:\r\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.list.contract.test.ts\r\n    getExportRegistry:\r\n      http: GET /api/export/registries/{taskCode}\r\n      requirements: [FR-007, FR-008, FR-013]\r\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007, AE-008, AE-016]\r\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/get-export-registry.handler.ts\r\n      db: [export_registries, export_registry_versions]\r\n      worker: []\r\n      audit: [REGISTRY_DETAIL]\r\n      file: []\r\n      tests:\r\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.detail.contract.test.ts\r\n    updateExportRegistry:\r\n      http: PUT /api/export/registries/{taskCode}\r\n      requirements: [FR-007, FR-008, FR-013]\r\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007, AE-008, AE-016]\r\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/update-export-registry.handler.ts\r\n      db: [export_registries, export_registry_versions, export_audit_logs]\r\n      worker: [updated config applies only to newly created tasks]\r\n      audit: [REGISTRY_UPDATE]\r\n      file: []\r\n      tests:\r\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.update.contract.test.ts\r\n        - tests/db/export-registry-snapshot.repository.test.ts\r\n    enableExportRegistry:\r\n      http: POST /api/export/registries/{taskCode}/enable\r\n      requirements: [FR-007]\r\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007]\r\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/enable-export-registry.handler.ts\r\n      db: [export_registries, export_audit_logs]\r\n      worker: []\r\n      audit: [REGISTRY_ENABLE]\r\n      file: []\r\n      tests:\r\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.enable.contract.test.ts\r\n    disableExportRegistry:\r\n      http: POST /api/export/registries/{taskCode}/disable\r\n      requirements: [FR-007]\r\n      acceptanceExamples: [AE-007]\r\n      handler: src/routes/export/registries/disable-export-registry.handler.ts\r\n      db: [export_registries, export_audit_logs]\r\n      worker: [future create requests must fail with TASK_DISABLED]\r\n      audit: [REGISTRY_DISABLE]\r\n      file: []\r\n      tests:\r\n        - tests/contract/export-registries.disable.contract.test.ts\r\npaths:\r\n  /export/tasks:\r\n    post:\r\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\r\n      summary: Create export task\r\n      description: |\r\n        Creates a PENDING export task when taskCode is registered and enabled.\r\n        clientRequestId is idempotent in scope tenantId + operatorId + taskCode + clientRequestId.\r\n      operationId: createExportTask\r\n      parameters:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\r\n      requestBody:\r\n        required: true\r\n        content:\r\n          application/json:\r\n            schema:\r\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/CreateExportTaskRequest\"\r\n            examples:\r\n              purchaseOrder:\r\n                summary: Purchase order export task\r\n                value:\r\n                  taskCode: purchase-order-export\r\n                  subsystemCode: purchase\r\n                  fileFormat: XLSX\r\n                  clientRequestId: req-20260513-0001\r\n                  queryParams:\r\n                    createdAtFrom: \"2026-05-01T00:00:00+08:00\"\r\n                    createdAtTo: \"2026-05-13T23:59:59+08:00\"\r\n                    orderStatus: APPROVED\r\n                    supplierId: SUP-001\r\n                    purchaseOrgId: ORG-001\r\n                    keyword: PO-2026\r\n      x-contract-errorResponses:\r\n        - TASK_DISABLED\r\n        - EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED\r\n        - QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID\r\n        - DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE\r\n        - FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\r\n        - MASKING_RULE_ERROR\r\n        - INTERNAL_ERROR\r\n      responses:\r\n        \"201\":\r\n          description: Task created.\r\n          content:\r\n            application/json:\r\n              schema:\r\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/CreateExportTaskResponseEnvelope\"\r\n              examples:\r\n                created:\r\n                  value:\r\n                    code: SUCCESS\r\n                    message: success\r\n                    data:\r\n                      taskId: exp_20260513_000001\r\n                      taskCode: purchase-order-export\r\n                      subsystemCode: purchase\r\n                      status: PENDING\r\n                      clientRequestId: req-20260513-0001\r\n                      idempotencyHit: false\r\n                      idempotencyScope: tenant-001:u001:purchase-order-export:req-20260513-0001\r\n                      requestDigest: sha256:request-digest\r\n                      configSnapshotDigest: sha256:config-digest\r\n                      attemptNo: 0\r\n                      createdAt: \"2026-05-13T10:00:00+08:00\"\r\n        \"200\":\r\n          description: Existing task returned for idempotent replay with identical request digest.\r\n          content:\r\n            application/json:\r\n              schema:\r\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/CreateExportTaskResponseEnvelope\"\r\n        \"400\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/CreateTaskBadRequest\"\r\n        \"401\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\r\n        \"403\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\r\n        \"404\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotRegistered\"\r\n        \"409\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/IdempotencyConflict\"\r\n        \"500\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/DatasourceUnavailable\"\r\n      x-contract-errorResponseStatus:\r\n        TASK_DISABLED: 400\r\n        QUERY_PARAMS_TOO_LARGE: 400\r\n        EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED: 400\r\n        DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE: 500\r\n        INTERNAL_ERROR: 500\r\n    get:\r\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\r\n      summary: Search task history\r\n      description: |\r\n        Returns paged task history. Normal users can only see their own tasks;\r\n        administrators can see global tasks according to roleCodes and orgScope.\r\n      operationId: listExportTasks\r\n      parameters:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\r\n        - name: taskCode\r\n          in: query\r\n          schema:\r\n            type: string\r\n        - name: status\r\n          in: query\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/TaskStatus\"\r\n        - name: createdBy\r\n          in: query\r\n          schema:\r\n            type: string\r\n        - name: createdAtFrom\r\n          in: query\r\n          schema:\r\n            type: string\r\n            format: date-time\r\n        - name: createdAtTo\r\n          in: query\r\n          schema:\r\n            type: string\r\n            format: date-time\r\n        - name: fileFormat\r\n          in: query\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/FileFormat\"\r\n        - name: subsystemCode\r\n          in: query\r\n          schema:\r\n            type: string\r\n        - name: page\r\n          in: query\r\n          schema:\r\n            type: integer\r\n            minimum: 1\r\n            default: 1\r\n        - name: pageSize\r\n          in: query\r\n          schema:\r\n            type: integer\r\n            minimum: 1\r\n            maximum: 100\r\n            default: 20\r\n      responses:\r\n        \"200\":\r\n          description: Paged task history.\r\n          content:\r\n            application/json:\r\n              schema:\r\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportTaskPageEnvelope\"\r\n        \"401\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\r\n        \"403\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\r\n        \"500\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/QueryExecutionError\"\r\n  /export/tasks/{taskId}:\r\n    get:\r\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\r\n      summary: Get task detail and progress\r\n      operationId: getExportTask\r\n      parameters:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskId\"\r\n      responses:\r\n        \"200\":\r\n          description: Task detail.\r\n          content:\r\n            application/json:\r\n              schema:\r\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportTaskDetailEnvelope\"\r\n              examples:\r\n                executing:\r\n                  value:\r\n                    code: SUCCESS\r\n                    message: success\r\n                    data:\r\n                      taskId: exp_20260513_000001\r\n                      taskCode: purchase-order-export\r\n                      subsystemCode: purchase\r\n                      status: EXECUTING\r\n                      totalCount: 100000\r\n                      processedCount: 20000\r\n                      progressPercent: 20.0\r\n                      fileFormat: ZIP\r\n                      attemptNo: 1\r\n                      requestId: req-20260513-0001\r\n                      requestDigest: sha256:request-digest\r\n                      configSnapshotDigest: sha256:config-digest\r\n                      createdBy: u001\r\n                      createdAt: \"2026-05-13T10:00:00+08:00\"\r\n                      updatedAt: \"2026-05-13T10:05:00+08:00\"\r\n        \"401\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\r\n        \"403\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\r\n        \"404\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotFound\"\r\n        \"500\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InternalError\"\r\n  /export/tasks/{taskId}/download:\r\n    get:\r\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\r\n      summary: Download exported file\r\n      description: |\r\n        The default mode returns a signed URL and file metadata. Stream delivery\r\n        is represented by application/octet-stream and equivalent metadata headers.\r\n      operationId: downloadExportTask\r\n      parameters:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskId\"\r\n        - name: mode\r\n          in: query\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/DeliveryMode\"\r\n            default: SIGNED_URL\r\n      responses:\r\n        \"200\":\r\n          description: Signed URL response or file stream.\r\n          headers:\r\n            X-Export-File-Name:\r\n              schema:\r\n                type: string\r\n            X-Export-File-Size:\r\n              schema:\r\n                type: integer\r\n                format: int64\r\n            X-Export-Checksum:\r\n              schema:\r\n                type: string\r\n            X-Export-Checksum-Algorithm:\r\n              schema:\r\n                type: string\r\n                enum: [SHA-256]\r\n            X-Export-Attempt-No:\r\n              schema:\r\n                type: integer\r\n          content:\r\n            application/json:\r\n              schema:\r\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/DownloadResponseEnvelope\"\r\n              examples:\r\n                signedUrl:\r\n                  value:\r\n                    code: SUCCESS\r\n                    message: success\r\n                    data:\r\n                      deliveryMode: SIGNED_URL\r\n                      downloadUrl: \"https://oss.example.com/signed-url\"\r\n                      expiresAt: \"2026-05-13T10:10:00+08:00\"\r\n                      fileName: purchase-order-export-20260513.zip\r\n                      fileSize: 1048576\r\n                      contentType: application/zip\r\n                      checksum: sha256:file-checksum\r\n                      checksumAlgorithm: SHA-256\r\n                      storageKey: exports/purchase/purchase-order-export/20260513/exp_20260513_000001/1/purchase-order-export-20260513.zip\r\n                      attemptNo: 1\r\n            application/octet-stream:\r\n              schema:\r\n                type: string\r\n                format: binary\r\n        \"400\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/FileNotReady\"\r\n        \"401\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\r\n        \"403\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\r\n        \"404\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotFound\"\r\n        \"410\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/FileExpired\"\r\n        \"500\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/FileVerifyError\"\r\n        \"502\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/ExportRenderError\"\r\n      x-contract-errorResponses:\r\n        - FILE_NOT_READY\r\n        - FILE_VERIFY_ERROR\r\n        - EXPORT_RENDER_ERROR\r\n        - INTERNAL_ERROR\r\n  /export/tasks/{taskId}/cancel:\r\n    post:\r\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\r\n      summary: Cancel export task\r\n      description: |\r\n        PENDING tasks can be canceled immediately. EXECUTING tasks accept cancel\r\n        intent and still return EXECUTING until the worker closes the task at a\r\n        batch boundary. The API never returns an internal cancel marker as a task status.\r\n      operationId: cancelExportTask\r\n      parameters:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskId\"\r\n      requestBody:\r\n        required: false\r\n        content:\r\n          application/json:\r\n            schema:\r\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/TaskActionRequest\"\r\n      responses:\r\n        \"200\":\r\n          description: Cancel accepted or completed.\r\n          content:\r\n            application/json:\r\n              schema:\r\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/TaskActionResponseEnvelope\"\r\n        \"400\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InvalidTaskState\"\r\n        \"401\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\r\n        \"403\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\r\n        \"404\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotFound\"\r\n        \"500\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InternalError\"\r\n  /export/tasks/{taskId}/retry:\r\n    post:\r\n      tags: [ExportTasks]\r\n      summary: Retry failed export task\r\n      description: |\r\n        Only FAILED tasks are retryable. Retry keeps the original taskId,\r\n        reuses the original config snapshot, increments attemptNo and creates no\r\n        second active execution attempt.\r\n      operationId: retryExportTask\r\n      parameters:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskId\"\r\n      requestBody:\r\n        required: false\r\n        content:\r\n          application/json:\r\n            schema:\r\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/TaskActionRequest\"\r\n      responses:\r\n        \"200\":\r\n          description: Retry accepted.\r\n          content:\r\n            application/json:\r\n              schema:\r\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/TaskActionResponseEnvelope\"\r\n        \"400\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InvalidTaskState\"\r\n        \"409\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/ActiveAttemptConflict\"\r\n        \"401\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\r\n        \"403\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\r\n        \"404\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotFound\"\r\n        \"500\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InternalError\"\r\n  /export/registries:\r\n    post:\r\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\r\n      summary: Create export registry\r\n      operationId: createExportRegistry\r\n      parameters:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\r\n      requestBody:\r\n        required: true\r\n        content:\r\n          application/json:\r\n            schema:\r\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryUpsertRequest\"\r\n            examples:\r\n              purchaseOrderRegistry:\r\n                value:\r\n                  taskCode: purchase-order-export\r\n                  subsystemCode: purchase\r\n                  displayName: Purchase order export\r\n                  enabled: true\r\n                  concurrencyLimit: 3\r\n                  fileRetentionDays: 15\r\n                  taskHistoryRetentionDays: 30\r\n                  singleFileMaxRows: 20000\r\n                  exportMaxRows: 100000\r\n                  supportedFormats: [XLSX, ZIP]\r\n                  datasourceCode: purchase_ro\r\n                  parameterSchema:\r\n                    required: [createdAtFrom, createdAtTo]\r\n                    properties:\r\n                      createdAtFrom:\r\n                        type: string\r\n                        format: date-time\r\n                      createdAtTo:\r\n                        type: string\r\n                        format: date-time\r\n                      orderStatus:\r\n                        type: string\r\n                      supplierId:\r\n                        type: string\r\n                      purchaseOrgId:\r\n                        type: string\r\n                      keyword:\r\n                        type: string\r\n                  queryTemplate:\r\n                    queryTemplateVersion: v1\r\n                    templateText: \"select ... where created_at between :createdAtFrom and :createdAtTo order by order_id asc\"\r\n                    allowedParameters: [createdAtFrom, createdAtTo, orderStatus, supplierId, purchaseOrgId, keyword]\r\n                  fieldMappings:\r\n                    - fieldCode: orderNo\r\n                      headerName: Order No\r\n                      fieldType: STRING\r\n                      orderNo: 1\r\n                      sensitive: false\r\n                      exportable: true\r\n                    - fieldCode: contactPhone\r\n                      headerName: Contact Phone\r\n                      fieldType: STRING\r\n                      orderNo: 10\r\n                      sensitive: true\r\n                      exportable: true\r\n                      maskingRuleCode: phone_mask\r\n                  maskingPolicy:\r\n                    rules:\r\n                      phone_mask:\r\n                        type: PHONE\r\n                        preservePrefix: 3\r\n                        preserveSuffix: 4\r\n                  dataScopeTemplate: \"tenant_id = :tenantId and org_id in (:orgScope)\"\r\n                  cursorField: orderId\r\n                  orderBy:\r\n                    - field: orderId\r\n                      direction: ASC\r\n                  batchSize: 1000\r\n      x-contract-errorResponses:\r\n        - QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID\r\n        - FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\r\n        - MASKING_RULE_ERROR\r\n        - REGISTRY_CONFLICT\r\n        - INTERNAL_ERROR\r\n      responses:\r\n        \"201\":\r\n          description: Registry created.\r\n          content:\r\n            application/json:\r\n              schema:\r\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryEnvelope\"\r\n        \"400\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/RegistryBadRequest\"\r\n        \"401\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\r\n        \"403\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\r\n        \"409\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/RegistryConflict\"\r\n        \"500\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/RegistryServerError\"\r\n    get:\r\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\r\n      summary: List export registries\r\n      operationId: listExportRegistries\r\n      parameters:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\r\n        - name: taskCode\r\n          in: query\r\n          schema:\r\n            type: string\r\n        - name: subsystemCode\r\n          in: query\r\n          schema:\r\n            type: string\r\n        - name: enabled\r\n          in: query\r\n          schema:\r\n            type: boolean\r\n        - name: page\r\n          in: query\r\n          schema:\r\n            type: integer\r\n            minimum: 1\r\n            default: 1\r\n        - name: pageSize\r\n          in: query\r\n          schema:\r\n            type: integer\r\n            minimum: 1\r\n            maximum: 100\r\n            default: 20\r\n      responses:\r\n        \"200\":\r\n          description: Paged registry list.\r\n          content:\r\n            application/json:\r\n              schema:\r\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryPageEnvelope\"\r\n        \"401\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\r\n        \"403\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\r\n        \"500\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InternalError\"\r\n  /export/registries/{taskCode}:\r\n    get:\r\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\r\n      summary: Get export registry\r\n      operationId: getExportRegistry\r\n      parameters:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskCode\"\r\n      responses:\r\n        \"200\":\r\n          description: Registry detail.\r\n          content:\r\n            application/json:\r\n              schema:\r\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryEnvelope\"\r\n        \"401\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\r\n        \"403\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\r\n        \"404\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotRegistered\"\r\n        \"500\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InternalError\"\r\n    put:\r\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\r\n      summary: Update export registry\r\n      description: Registry updates only affect tasks created after the update.\r\n      operationId: updateExportRegistry\r\n      parameters:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskCode\"\r\n      requestBody:\r\n        required: true\r\n        content:\r\n          application/json:\r\n            schema:\r\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryUpsertRequest\"\r\n      x-contract-errorResponses:\r\n        - QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID\r\n        - FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\r\n        - MASKING_RULE_ERROR\r\n        - INTERNAL_ERROR\r\n      responses:\r\n        \"200\":\r\n          description: Registry updated.\r\n          content:\r\n            application/json:\r\n              schema:\r\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryEnvelope\"\r\n        \"400\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/RegistryBadRequest\"\r\n        \"401\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\r\n        \"403\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\r\n        \"404\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotRegistered\"\r\n        \"500\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/RegistryServerError\"\r\n  /export/registries/{taskCode}/enable:\r\n    post:\r\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\r\n      summary: Enable export registry\r\n      operationId: enableExportRegistry\r\n      parameters:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskCode\"\r\n      responses:\r\n        \"200\":\r\n          description: Registry enabled.\r\n          content:\r\n            application/json:\r\n              schema:\r\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryEnvelope\"\r\n        \"401\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\r\n        \"403\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\r\n        \"404\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotRegistered\"\r\n        \"500\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InternalError\"\r\n  /export/registries/{taskCode}/disable:\r\n    post:\r\n      tags: [ExportRegistries]\r\n      summary: Disable export registry\r\n      operationId: disableExportRegistry\r\n      parameters:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOperatorId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XTenantId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRoleCodes\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XOrgScope\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/XRequestId\"\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/parameters/TaskCode\"\r\n      responses:\r\n        \"200\":\r\n          description: Registry disabled.\r\n          content:\r\n            application/json:\r\n              schema:\r\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryEnvelope\"\r\n        \"401\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/AuthContextMissing\"\r\n        \"403\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/PermissionDenied\"\r\n        \"404\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/TaskNotRegistered\"\r\n        \"500\":\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/responses/InternalError\"\r\ncomponents:\r\n  securitySchemes:\r\n    OperatorId:\r\n      type: apiKey\r\n      in: header\r\n      name: X-Operator-Id\r\n      description: Authenticated operator id forwarded by gateway or caller.\r\n    TenantId:\r\n      type: apiKey\r\n      in: header\r\n      name: X-Tenant-Id\r\n      description: Tenant id forwarded by gateway or caller.\r\n    RoleCodes:\r\n      type: apiKey\r\n      in: header\r\n      name: X-Role-Codes\r\n      description: Comma-separated role codes forwarded by gateway or caller.\r\n    OrgScope:\r\n      type: apiKey\r\n      in: header\r\n      name: X-Org-Scope\r\n      description: Organization scope forwarded by gateway or caller.\r\n    RequestId:\r\n      type: apiKey\r\n      in: header\r\n      name: X-Request-Id\r\n      description: Request id used by audit logs and task events.\r\n  parameters:\r\n    XOperatorId:\r\n      name: X-Operator-Id\r\n      in: header\r\n      required: true\r\n      schema:\r\n        type: string\r\n      description: Authenticated operator id.\r\n    XTenantId:\r\n      name: X-Tenant-Id\r\n      in: header\r\n      required: true\r\n      schema:\r\n        type: string\r\n      description: Tenant id for task visibility and data scope.\r\n    XRoleCodes:\r\n      name: X-Role-Codes\r\n      in: header\r\n      required: true\r\n      schema:\r\n        type: string\r\n      description: Comma-separated role codes.\r\n    XOrgScope:\r\n      name: X-Org-Scope\r\n      in: header\r\n      required: true\r\n      schema:\r\n        type: string\r\n      description: Organization scope expression or encoded scope list.\r\n    XRequestId:\r\n      name: X-Request-Id\r\n      in: header\r\n      required: true\r\n      schema:\r\n        type: string\r\n      description: Upstream request id used by audit logs and task events.\r\n    TaskId:\r\n      name: taskId\r\n      in: path\r\n      required: true\r\n      schema:\r\n        type: string\r\n    TaskCode:\r\n      name: taskCode\r\n      in: path\r\n      required: true\r\n      schema:\r\n        type: string\r\n  responses:\r\n    AuthContextMissing:\r\n      description: Required auth context is missing or malformed.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            authMissing:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: AUTH_CONTEXT_MISSING\r\n                message: auth context missing\r\n                data: null\r\n    PermissionDenied:\r\n      description: Operator has no permission for the task, registry or file.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            denied:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: PERMISSION_DENIED\r\n                message: permission denied\r\n                data: null\r\n    TaskNotFound:\r\n      description: Task not found or invisible to current operator.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            notFound:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: TASK_NOT_FOUND\r\n                message: task not found\r\n                data: null\r\n    TaskNotRegistered:\r\n      description: taskCode is not registered.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            notRegistered:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: TASK_NOT_REGISTERED\r\n                message: task code not registered\r\n                data: null\r\n    CreateTaskBadRequest:\r\n      description: Create task request is invalid, disabled or exceeds configured limits.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            validation:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: VALIDATION_ERROR\r\n                message: validation failed\r\n                data: null\r\n                errors:\r\n                  - field: taskCode\r\n                    reason: required\r\n            taskDisabled:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: TASK_DISABLED\r\n                message: task code is disabled\r\n                data:\r\n                  taskCode: purchase-order-export\r\n            queryParamsTooLarge:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: QUERY_PARAMS_TOO_LARGE\r\n                message: queryParams exceeds 32768 bytes\r\n                data: null\r\n            exportLimitExceeded:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED\r\n                message: export limit exceeded\r\n                data:\r\n                  exportMaxRows: 100000\r\n    IdempotencyConflict:\r\n      description: Same idempotency scope with different request digest.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            conflict:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: IDEMPOTENCY_CONFLICT\r\n                message: clientRequestId conflicts with a different request digest\r\n                data:\r\n                  idempotencyScope: tenant-001:u001:purchase-order-export:req-20260513-0001\r\n    InvalidTaskState:\r\n      description: Operation is not allowed for current official task status.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            invalidRetry:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: INVALID_TASK_STATE\r\n                message: current task status does not allow this operation\r\n                data:\r\n                  status: EXECUTING\r\n    ActiveAttemptConflict:\r\n      description: Another active execution attempt already exists.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            activeAttempt:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: ACTIVE_ATTEMPT_CONFLICT\r\n                message: active execution attempt already exists\r\n                data:\r\n                  taskId: exp_20260513_000001\r\n                  attemptNo: 1\r\n    FileExpired:\r\n      description: File is expired or marked as not downloadable.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            expired:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: FILE_EXPIRED\r\n                message: file expired\r\n                data: null\r\n    FileNotReady:\r\n      description: File is not published or the task is not completed yet.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            notReady:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: FILE_NOT_READY\r\n                message: file is not ready for download\r\n                data:\r\n                  status: EXECUTING\r\n    FileVerifyError:\r\n      description: File upload, metadata or checksum verification failed before publish.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            verifyFailed:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: FILE_VERIFY_ERROR\r\n                message: file verification failed\r\n                data:\r\n                  checksumAlgorithm: SHA-256\r\n    DatasourceUnavailable:\r\n      description: Datasource or datasource credential is unavailable.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            datasourceUnavailable:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE\r\n                message: datasource unavailable\r\n                data:\r\n                  datasourceCode: purchase_ro\r\n    QueryExecutionError:\r\n      description: Query execution failed, batch retries exhausted or cursor contract violated.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            queryFailed:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR\r\n                message: query execution failed\r\n                data:\r\n                  cursorField: orderId\r\n    RegistryBadRequest:\r\n      description: Registry request is invalid, exceeds limits, or contains invalid field/masking configuration.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            validation:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: VALIDATION_ERROR\r\n                message: validation failed\r\n                data: null\r\n            exportLimitExceeded:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED\r\n                message: export limit exceeded\r\n                data:\r\n                  exportMaxRows: 100000\r\n            fieldMappingInvalid:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\r\n                message: field mapping invalid\r\n                data:\r\n                  fieldCode: contactPhone\r\n            maskingRuleError:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: MASKING_RULE_ERROR\r\n                message: masking rule error\r\n                data:\r\n                  maskingRuleCode: phone_mask\r\n    RegistryServerError:\r\n      description: Registry contract references an invalid query template, datasource, field mapping or masking backend.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            queryTemplateInvalid:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID\r\n                message: query template invalid\r\n                data:\r\n                  taskCode: purchase-order-export\r\n            datasourceUnavailable:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE\r\n                message: datasource unavailable\r\n                data:\r\n                  datasourceCode: purchase_ro\r\n            fieldMappingInvalid:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\r\n                message: field mapping invalid\r\n                data:\r\n                  fieldCode: contactPhone\r\n            maskingRuleError:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: MASKING_RULE_ERROR\r\n                message: masking rule error\r\n                data:\r\n                  maskingRuleCode: phone_mask\r\n    ExportRenderError:\r\n      description: XLSX or ZIP render failed.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            renderFailed:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: EXPORT_RENDER_ERROR\r\n                message: export render error\r\n                data:\r\n                  fileFormat: ZIP\r\n    RegistryConflict:\r\n      description: Registry taskCode already exists or conflicts with immutable fields.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            duplicate:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: REGISTRY_CONFLICT\r\n                message: taskCode already exists\r\n                data: null\r\n    InternalError:\r\n      description: Unclassified server-side error. Specific platform errors should use a more precise response when known.\r\n      content:\r\n        application/json:\r\n          schema:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ErrorEnvelope\"\r\n          examples:\r\n            internalError:\r\n              value:\r\n                code: INTERNAL_ERROR\r\n                message: internal error\r\n                data: null\r\n  schemas:\r\n    ResponseCode:\r\n      type: string\r\n      enum:\r\n        - SUCCESS\r\n        - VALIDATION_ERROR\r\n        - AUTH_CONTEXT_MISSING\r\n        - PERMISSION_DENIED\r\n        - TASK_NOT_FOUND\r\n        - TASK_NOT_REGISTERED\r\n        - TASK_DISABLED\r\n        - QUERY_PARAMS_TOO_LARGE\r\n        - IDEMPOTENCY_CONFLICT\r\n        - INVALID_TASK_STATE\r\n        - FILE_EXPIRED\r\n        - FILE_NOT_READY\r\n        - FILE_VERIFY_ERROR\r\n        - QUERY_TEMPLATE_INVALID\r\n        - DATASOURCE_UNAVAILABLE\r\n        - QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR\r\n        - FIELD_MAPPING_INVALID\r\n        - MASKING_RULE_ERROR\r\n        - EXPORT_RENDER_ERROR\r\n        - EXPORT_LIMIT_EXCEEDED\r\n        - REGISTRY_CONFLICT\r\n        - ACTIVE_ATTEMPT_CONFLICT\r\n        - INTERNAL_ERROR\r\n    TaskStatus:\r\n      type: string\r\n      description: Official public task status. Internal cancel flags are not valid values.\r\n      enum: [PENDING, EXECUTING, COMPLETED, FAILED, CANCELED, EXPIRED]\r\n    FileFormat:\r\n      type: string\r\n      enum: [XLSX, ZIP]\r\n    DeliveryMode:\r\n      type: string\r\n      enum: [SIGNED_URL, STREAM]\r\n    Envelope:\r\n      type: object\r\n      required: [code, message]\r\n      properties:\r\n        code:\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ResponseCode\"\r\n        message:\r\n          type: string\r\n    ErrorEnvelope:\r\n      allOf:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/schemas/Envelope\"\r\n        - type: object\r\n          properties:\r\n            data:\r\n              type: object\r\n              nullable: true\r\n              additionalProperties: true\r\n            errors:\r\n              type: array\r\n              items:\r\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/FieldError\"\r\n    FieldError:\r\n      type: object\r\n      required: [field, reason]\r\n      properties:\r\n        field:\r\n          type: string\r\n        reason:\r\n          type: string\r\n    CreateExportTaskRequest:\r\n      type: object\r\n      required: [taskCode, subsystemCode, fileFormat, queryParams]\r\n      properties:\r\n        taskCode:\r\n          type: string\r\n        subsystemCode:\r\n          type: string\r\n        fileFormat:\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/FileFormat\"\r\n        clientRequestId:\r\n          type: string\r\n          maxLength: 128\r\n          description: Optional idempotency key scoped by tenantId/operatorId/taskCode.\r\n        queryParams:\r\n          type: object\r\n          additionalProperties: true\r\n          description: Must match registry parameter schema and must not exceed 32768 bytes after canonical JSON serialization.\r\n        deliveryPreference:\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/DeliveryMode\"\r\n    CreateExportTaskResponseEnvelope:\r\n      allOf:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/schemas/Envelope\"\r\n        - type: object\r\n          required: [data]\r\n          properties:\r\n            data:\r\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/CreateExportTaskResponse\"\r\n    CreateExportTaskResponse:\r\n      type: object\r\n      required:\r\n        - taskId\r\n        - taskCode\r\n        - subsystemCode\r\n        - status\r\n        - idempotencyScope\r\n        - requestDigest\r\n        - configSnapshotDigest\r\n        - attemptNo\r\n        - createdAt\r\n      properties:\r\n        taskId:\r\n          type: string\r\n        taskCode:\r\n          type: string\r\n        subsystemCode:\r\n          type: string\r\n        status:\r\n          type: string\r\n          enum: [PENDING]\r\n        clientRequestId:\r\n          type: string\r\n        idempotencyHit:\r\n          type: boolean\r\n        idempotencyScope:\r\n          type: string\r\n          description: Stable success-response evidence for the tenantId + operatorId + taskCode + clientRequestId idempotency scope.\r\n        requestDigest:\r\n          type: string\r\n        configSnapshotDigest:\r\n          type: string\r\n        attemptNo:\r\n          type: integer\r\n          minimum: 0\r\n        createdAt:\r\n          type: string\r\n          format: date-time\r\n    ExportTaskDetailEnvelope:\r\n      allOf:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/schemas/Envelope\"\r\n        - type: object\r\n          required: [data]\r\n          properties:\r\n            data:\r\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportTaskDetail\"\r\n    ExportTaskDetail:\r\n      type: object\r\n      required:\r\n        - taskId\r\n        - taskCode\r\n        - subsystemCode\r\n        - status\r\n        - totalCount\r\n        - processedCount\r\n        - progressPercent\r\n        - attemptNo\r\n        - requestId\r\n        - requestDigest\r\n        - configSnapshotDigest\r\n        - createdBy\r\n        - createdAt\r\n        - updatedAt\r\n      properties:\r\n        taskId:\r\n          type: string\r\n        taskCode:\r\n          type: string\r\n        subsystemCode:\r\n          type: string\r\n        status:\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/TaskStatus\"\r\n        totalCount:\r\n          type: integer\r\n          format: int64\r\n          minimum: 0\r\n        processedCount:\r\n          type: integer\r\n          format: int64\r\n          minimum: 0\r\n        progressPercent:\r\n          type: number\r\n          minimum: 0\r\n          maximum: 100\r\n        fileFormat:\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/FileFormat\"\r\n        attemptNo:\r\n          type: integer\r\n          minimum: 0\r\n        errorCode:\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ResponseCode\"\r\n        errorMessage:\r\n          type: string\r\n        failureStage:\r\n          type: string\r\n        lastSuccessStage:\r\n          type: string\r\n        requestId:\r\n          type: string\r\n        requestDigest:\r\n          type: string\r\n        configSnapshotDigest:\r\n          type: string\r\n        createdBy:\r\n          type: string\r\n        createdAt:\r\n          type: string\r\n          format: date-time\r\n        updatedAt:\r\n          type: string\r\n          format: date-time\r\n        file:\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/FileMetadata\"\r\n        batchCheckpoint:\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/BatchCheckpoint\"\r\n        recentEvents:\r\n          type: array\r\n          items:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/TaskEvent\"\r\n        auditEvents:\r\n          type: array\r\n          items:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/AuditEvent\"\r\n    ExportTaskPageEnvelope:\r\n      allOf:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/schemas/Envelope\"\r\n        - type: object\r\n          required: [data]\r\n          properties:\r\n            data:\r\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportTaskPage\"\r\n    ExportTaskPage:\r\n      type: object\r\n      required: [items, page, pageSize, total]\r\n      properties:\r\n        items:\r\n          type: array\r\n          items:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportTaskDetail\"\r\n        page:\r\n          type: integer\r\n        pageSize:\r\n          type: integer\r\n        total:\r\n          type: integer\r\n          format: int64\r\n    DownloadResponseEnvelope:\r\n      allOf:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/schemas/Envelope\"\r\n        - type: object\r\n          required: [data]\r\n          properties:\r\n            data:\r\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/DownloadResponse\"\r\n    DownloadResponse:\r\n      allOf:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/schemas/FileMetadata\"\r\n        - type: object\r\n          required: [deliveryMode, expiresAt]\r\n          properties:\r\n            deliveryMode:\r\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/DeliveryMode\"\r\n            downloadUrl:\r\n              type: string\r\n              format: uri\r\n            expiresAt:\r\n              type: string\r\n              format: date-time\r\n    FileMetadata:\r\n      type: object\r\n      required:\r\n        - fileName\r\n        - fileSize\r\n        - contentType\r\n        - checksum\r\n        - checksumAlgorithm\r\n        - storageKey\r\n        - expiresAt\r\n        - attemptNo\r\n      properties:\r\n        fileName:\r\n          type: string\r\n        fileSize:\r\n          type: integer\r\n          format: int64\r\n        contentType:\r\n          type: string\r\n        tempStorageKey:\r\n          type: string\r\n        publishedStorageKey:\r\n          type: string\r\n        storageKey:\r\n          type: string\r\n        expiresAt:\r\n          type: string\r\n          format: date-time\r\n          description: Published file retention expiry time. Signed URL responses also use expiresAt for URL expiry.\r\n        checksum:\r\n          type: string\r\n        checksumAlgorithm:\r\n          type: string\r\n          enum: [SHA-256]\r\n        checksumVerifiedAt:\r\n          type: string\r\n          format: date-time\r\n        publishedAt:\r\n          type: string\r\n          format: date-time\r\n        deliveryReadyAt:\r\n          type: string\r\n          format: date-time\r\n        attemptNo:\r\n          type: integer\r\n          minimum: 1\r\n    TaskActionRequest:\r\n      type: object\r\n      properties:\r\n        reason:\r\n          type: string\r\n          maxLength: 500\r\n    TaskActionResponseEnvelope:\r\n      allOf:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/schemas/Envelope\"\r\n        - type: object\r\n          required: [data]\r\n          properties:\r\n            data:\r\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/TaskActionResponse\"\r\n    TaskActionResponse:\r\n      type: object\r\n      required: [taskId, status, attemptNo, acceptedAt]\r\n      properties:\r\n        taskId:\r\n          type: string\r\n        status:\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/TaskStatus\"\r\n        attemptNo:\r\n          type: integer\r\n        cancelAccepted:\r\n          type: boolean\r\n          description: True means an EXECUTING task will stop at a batch boundary; this is not a task status.\r\n        retryAccepted:\r\n          type: boolean\r\n        configSnapshotDigest:\r\n          type: string\r\n        acceptedAt:\r\n          type: string\r\n          format: date-time\r\n    ExportRegistryUpsertRequest:\r\n      type: object\r\n      required:\r\n        - taskCode\r\n        - subsystemCode\r\n        - displayName\r\n        - enabled\r\n        - concurrencyLimit\r\n        - fileRetentionDays\r\n        - taskHistoryRetentionDays\r\n        - singleFileMaxRows\r\n        - exportMaxRows\r\n        - supportedFormats\r\n        - datasourceCode\r\n        - parameterSchema\r\n        - queryTemplate\r\n        - fieldMappings\r\n        - maskingPolicy\r\n        - dataScopeTemplate\r\n        - cursorField\r\n        - orderBy\r\n        - batchSize\r\n      properties:\r\n        taskCode:\r\n          type: string\r\n        subsystemCode:\r\n          type: string\r\n        displayName:\r\n          type: string\r\n        enabled:\r\n          type: boolean\r\n        concurrencyLimit:\r\n          type: integer\r\n          minimum: 1\r\n        fileRetentionDays:\r\n          type: integer\r\n          minimum: 1\r\n          default: 15\r\n        taskHistoryRetentionDays:\r\n          type: integer\r\n          minimum: 1\r\n          default: 30\r\n        singleFileMaxRows:\r\n          type: integer\r\n          minimum: 1\r\n          default: 20000\r\n        exportMaxRows:\r\n          type: integer\r\n          minimum: 1\r\n          default: 100000\r\n        supportedFormats:\r\n          type: array\r\n          minItems: 1\r\n          items:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/FileFormat\"\r\n        datasourceCode:\r\n          type: string\r\n          description: Must reference a registered read-only datasource or data platform dataset.\r\n        parameterSchema:\r\n          type: object\r\n          additionalProperties: true\r\n        queryTemplate:\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/QueryTemplateContract\"\r\n        fieldMappings:\r\n          type: array\r\n          minItems: 1\r\n          items:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/FieldMapping\"\r\n        maskingPolicy:\r\n          type: object\r\n          additionalProperties: true\r\n          description: Required masking policy. Any fieldMappings item with sensitive=true must reference a maskingRuleCode covered by this policy.\r\n        dataScopeTemplate:\r\n          type: string\r\n          description: Data scope expression using tenantId, operatorId, roleCodes and orgScope.\r\n        cursorField:\r\n          type: string\r\n        orderBy:\r\n          type: array\r\n          minItems: 1\r\n          items:\r\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/OrderBy\"\r\n        batchSize:\r\n          type: integer\r\n          minimum: 1\r\n    ExportRegistryEnvelope:\r\n      allOf:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/schemas/Envelope\"\r\n        - type: object\r\n          required: [data]\r\n          properties:\r\n            data:\r\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistry\"\r\n    ExportRegistryPageEnvelope:\r\n      allOf:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/schemas/Envelope\"\r\n        - type: object\r\n          required: [data]\r\n          properties:\r\n            data:\r\n              type: object\r\n              required: [items, page, pageSize, total]\r\n              properties:\r\n                items:\r\n                  type: array\r\n                  items:\r\n                    $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistry\"\r\n                page:\r\n                  type: integer\r\n                pageSize:\r\n                  type: integer\r\n                total:\r\n                  type: integer\r\n                  format: int64\r\n    ExportRegistry:\r\n      allOf:\r\n        - $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ExportRegistryUpsertRequest\"\r\n        - type: object\r\n          required:\r\n            - configSnapshotDigest\r\n            - parameterSchemaDigest\r\n            - fieldMappingDigest\r\n            - maskingPolicyDigest\r\n            - updatedAt\r\n            - updatedBy\r\n          properties:\r\n            configSnapshotDigest:\r\n              type: string\r\n            parameterSchemaDigest:\r\n              type: string\r\n              description: Digest of the effective parameter schema used by future config snapshots.\r\n            fieldMappingDigest:\r\n              type: string\r\n              description: Digest of ordered field mappings and exportable whitelist.\r\n            maskingPolicyDigest:\r\n              type: string\r\n              description: Digest of masking policy and sensitive field rules.\r\n            updatedAt:\r\n              type: string\r\n              format: date-time\r\n            updatedBy:\r\n              type: string\r\n    QueryTemplateContract:\r\n      type: object\r\n      required: [queryTemplateVersion, templateText, allowedParameters]\r\n      properties:\r\n        queryTemplateVersion:\r\n          type: string\r\n        templateText:\r\n          type: string\r\n          description: Parameterized query template. Raw SQL from callers is forbidden.\r\n        allowedParameters:\r\n          type: array\r\n          items:\r\n            type: string\r\n    FieldMapping:\r\n      type: object\r\n      required: [fieldCode, headerName, fieldType, orderNo, sensitive, exportable]\r\n      properties:\r\n        fieldCode:\r\n          type: string\r\n        headerName:\r\n          type: string\r\n        fieldType:\r\n          type: string\r\n          enum: [STRING, NUMBER, DECIMAL, DATETIME, DATE, BOOLEAN]\r\n        orderNo:\r\n          type: integer\r\n          minimum: 1\r\n        sensitive:\r\n          type: boolean\r\n        exportable:\r\n          type: boolean\r\n        maskingRuleCode:\r\n          type: string\r\n    OrderBy:\r\n      type: object\r\n      required: [field, direction]\r\n      properties:\r\n        field:\r\n          type: string\r\n        direction:\r\n          type: string\r\n          enum: [ASC, DESC]\r\n    BatchCheckpoint:\r\n      type: object\r\n      required:\r\n        - attemptNo\r\n        - lockOwner\r\n        - lockExpireAt\r\n        - leaseRenewedAt\r\n        - databaseTime\r\n      properties:\r\n        lastCursor:\r\n          type: string\r\n        processedCount:\r\n          type: integer\r\n          format: int64\r\n        filePartNo:\r\n          type: integer\r\n        attemptNo:\r\n          type: integer\r\n        batchSize:\r\n          type: integer\r\n        batchRowCount:\r\n          type: integer\r\n        retryCount:\r\n          type: integer\r\n        backoffMs:\r\n          type: integer\r\n        lockOwner:\r\n          type: string\r\n          description: Worker identity that owns the database lease for the current attempt.\r\n        lockExpireAt:\r\n          type: string\r\n          format: date-time\r\n          description: Lease expiry based on database time; default lease is five minutes unless registry config overrides it.\r\n        leaseRenewedAt:\r\n          type: string\r\n          format: date-time\r\n          description: Last successful lease renewal time based on database time.\r\n        databaseTime:\r\n          type: string\r\n          format: date-time\r\n          description: Database clock snapshot used for lock acquisition, renewal and takeover decisions.\r\n        takeoverRule:\r\n          type: string\r\n          description: Workers may take over only after database time is later than lockExpireAt; takeover keeps the same attemptNo.\r\n    AuditEvent:\r\n      type: object\r\n      required:\r\n        - taskId\r\n        - taskCode\r\n        - subsystemCode\r\n        - operatorId\r\n        - action\r\n        - result\r\n        - errorCode\r\n        - requestId\r\n        - occurredAt\r\n      properties:\r\n        taskId:\r\n          type: string\r\n        taskCode:\r\n          type: string\r\n        subsystemCode:\r\n          type: string\r\n        operatorId:\r\n          type: string\r\n        action:\r\n          type: string\r\n          enum:\r\n            - CREATE\r\n            - QUERY_HISTORY\r\n            - DETAIL_VIEW\r\n            - DISPATCH\r\n            - EXECUTE_START\r\n            - EXECUTE_SUCCESS\r\n            - EXECUTE_FAILED\r\n            - CANCEL_REQUEST\r\n            - CANCEL_DONE\r\n            - RETRY_REQUEST\r\n            - DOWNLOAD\r\n            - EXPIRE_MARK\r\n            - CLEANUP_FAILED\r\n            - REGISTRY_CREATE\r\n            - REGISTRY_QUERY\r\n            - REGISTRY_DETAIL\r\n            - REGISTRY_UPDATE\r\n            - REGISTRY_ENABLE\r\n            - REGISTRY_DISABLE\r\n        result:\r\n          type: string\r\n          enum: [SUCCESS, FAILED, ACCEPTED]\r\n        errorCode:\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ResponseCode\"\r\n        requestId:\r\n          type: string\r\n        occurredAt:\r\n          type: string\r\n          format: date-time\r\n    TaskEvent:\r\n      type: object\r\n      required: [taskId, attemptNo, eventType, requestId, occurredAt]\r\n      properties:\r\n        taskId:\r\n          type: string\r\n        attemptNo:\r\n          type: integer\r\n        eventType:\r\n          type: string\r\n          enum:\r\n            - QUERY_READY\r\n            - QUERY_BATCH_DONE\r\n            - FILE_PART_WRITTEN\r\n            - PACKAGE_DONE\r\n            - FILE_VERIFIED\r\n            - DELIVERY_READY\r\n        requestId:\r\n          type: string\r\n        datasourceCode:\r\n          type: string\r\n        queryTemplateVersion:\r\n          type: string\r\n        batchCheckpoint:\r\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/BatchCheckpoint\"\r\n        occurredAt:\r\n          type: string\r\n          format: date-time\r\n\ncodex\n`contracts/README.md` 自身声明契约复核的最小验证还包括 Redocly OpenAPI lint，但 Driver 只给了空白检查。我会补跑这个契约可解析性验证，确认当前证据是否可信。\nexec\n\"C:\\\\Program Files\\\\PowerShell\\\\7\\\\pwsh.exe\" -Command \u0027powershell -NoProfile -Command \"npx --yes @redocly/cli@1.34.5 lint contracts/openapi.yaml\"\u0027 in E:\\2026\\alpha-project\\longgang-codex-driver\n succeeded in 8283ms:\n\n    \u001b[33m╔\u001b[33m═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════\u001b[33m╗\u001b[39m\n    \u001b[33m║                                                       ║\u001b[39m\n    \u001b[33m║\u001b[39m  A new version of \u001b[36mR